, 0x03, 0x22, 0x00, 0x00, 0x5a, 0x22, 0x00, 0x00, 0x44, 0x23, 0x00, 0x00, 0x26, 0x24, 0x00, 0x00, 0x9f, 0x24, 0x00, 0x00, 0x2e, 0x25, 0x00, 0x00, 0x71, 0x25, 0x00, 0x00, 0xb7, 0x25, 0x00, 0x00, 0x23, 0x26, 0x00, 0x00, 0x8a, 0x26, 0x00, 0x00, 0xff, 0x26, 0x00, 0x00, 0xbf, 0x27, 0x00, 0x00, 0x30, 0x28, 0x00, 0x00, 0xd0, 0x28, 0x00, 0x00, 0x4e, 0x29, 0x00, 0x00, 0xf4, 0x29, 0x00, 0x00, 0x22, 0x2a, 0x00, 0x00, 0x69, 0x2a, 0x00, 0x00, 0xb9, 0x2a, 0x00, 0x00, 0x14, 0x2b, 0x00, 0x00, 0x5e, 0x2b, 0x00, 0x00, 0x7d, 0x2b, 0x00, 0x00, 0xb9, 0x2b, 0x00, 0x00, 0xdc, 0x2b, 0x00, 0x00, 0xff, 0x2b, 0x00, 0x00, 0x23, 0x2c, 0x00, 0x00, 0x56, 0x2c, 0x00, 0x00, 0xac, 0x2c, 0x00, 0x00, 0xe9, 0x2c, 0x00, 0x00, 0x50, 0x2d, 0x00, 0x00, 0x05, 0x2e, 0x00, 0x00, 0x6e, 0x2e, 0x00, 0x00, 0xed, 0x2e, 0x00, 0x00, 0xfe, 0x2f, 0x00, 0x00, 0x4f, 0x30, 0x00, 0x00, 0x86, 0x30, 0x00, 0x00, 0xd3, 0x30, 0x00, 0x00, 0x1c, 0x31, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x32, 0x00, 0x00, 0x9c, 0x32, 0x00, 0x00, 0x13, 0x33, 0x00, 0x00, 0x79, 0x34, 0x00, 0x00, 0x90, 0x35, 0x00, 0x00, 0x14, 0x36, 0x00, 0x00, 0x5c, 0x36, 0x00, 0x00, 0xc7, 0x36, 0x00, 0x00, 0x01, 0x37, 0x00, 0x00, 0x74, 0x37, 0x00, 0x00, 0xef, 0x37, 0x00, 0x00, 0xf0, 0x37, 0x00, 0x00, 0x7d, 0x38, 0x00, 0x00, 0x7e, 0x38, 0x00, 0x00, 0x47, 0x39, 0x00, 0x00, 0x96, 0x39, 0x00, 0x00, 0xee, 0x39, 0x00, 0x00, 0xd4, 0x3a, 0x00, 0x00, 0x5b, 0x3b, 0x00, 0x00, 0xfc, 0x3b, 0x00, 0x00, 0x03, 0x00, 0x91
    .string "Ew! What is that? Is that a\ncaterpillar? It's disgusting!\nHey, kid! I'll just let you\ntake care of this one!${UNK_03008D}What are you doing, talking to me at a\ntime like this! You've got work to do!${UNK_03008E}My word! It has spikes, it jumps...\nWhat can't it do!? Ah, such a bother!${UNK_03008D}Ahhhh! Watch your feet!! Such an\ninhospitable monster this is!${UNK_03008D}This must be another guardian,\n"
    .string "wouldn't you agree?\nHm... Knock him down, and he just gets\nback up again!\n{PLAYER}! It's time to see if you\ncan knock him down for good!${UNK_03008D}{PLAYER}! If you need my help, you\nknow where to find me!\nJust give me a shout, and I'll see\nwhat I can do to lend a...er...beak.${UNK_030092}{PLAYER}, I would imagine that you can\ntake this thing out with ease now.\nJust remember everything I've\n"
    .string "taught you!${UNK_030091}This weather's miserable! I think I'm\ncatching a cold...\nAh...ah...achoo!\n\nOh, don't worry about me, {PLAYER}.\nI'm sure I'll be just fine... Sniffle...${UNK_030092}These sky-flying rays will be no match\nfor my {COLOR}{GREEN}White Sword{COLOR}{WHITE}!\nI mean your {COLOR}{GREEN}White Sword{COLOR}{WHITE}, {PLAYER}!!${UNK_030091}Maybe I forgot to mention it,\nbut I'm not so good with heights...\n"
    .string "But this thing would be a piece of cake\non land, am I not right?\nWell, no point worrying about that now!${UNK_030092}These Black Knights are\nin {COLOR}{RED}Vaati{COLOR}{WHITE}'s service!\nExercise caution, {PLAYER}!${UNK_03008D}If we don't stop {COLOR}{RED}Vaati{COLOR}{WHITE} here, {COLOR}{RED}Princess\nZelda{COLOR}{WHITE}--and all of Hyrule--is done for!\nWe cannot allow that to happen,\n{PLAYER}!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}So this is the true form\nof the {COLOR}{YELLOW}sorcerer {COLOR}{RED}Vaati{COLOR}{WHITE}!\nSo dark... So powerful... So evil!${UNK_03008E}{PLAYER}, judging by the look in your\neyes, I'd say you've made up your mind!\nExcellent! Perhaps now, we are ready\nto face {COLOR}{RED}Vaati{COLOR}{WHITE}!${UNK_030092}He's mad with power! He's nothing but\na swirling mass of raw chaos now!\n"
    .string "He will consume everything and reduce\nthe world to darkness!\nIf we let him go now, he will engulf\nthe world in an eternal night!${UNK_03008D}What are you doing!? We've no\ntime for any of your nonsense!${UNK_030092}Waugh! What a hideous face!\n...It's no good, {PLAYER}.\nWe tried to settle this peacefully, but\nsome people can't be reasoned with...${UNK_03008D}{PLAYER}, save your breath!\n"
    .string "Fight now and talk later!${UNK_030091}So this would be the {COLOR}{RED}Deepwood\nShrine{COLOR}{WHITE} the Minish elder spoke of...\nHe...said something about there being\nmonsters inside, didn't he?\nHe-Hey now! No reason to be afraid or\nanything... I'll be waiting right here.\nNo, wait! What am I saying!? I'm not\nletting you leave me alone out here!${UNK_030091}Wow... It's hot in here! Come on!\n"
    .string "Let's not stand around wasting time!\nFind that {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE}, so we can\nget out of here!${UNK_03008E}Hm. To think the ruins were hidden\nwithin this cliff the whole time!\nWatch your step, {PLAYER}. There\nmay be traps in here.${UNK_03008D}Who knew there'd be someplace like this\n"
    .string "behind one of the town's fountains?!\nWell, let's get moving and see if we can\nfind that item those Minish mentioned.${UNK_030091}Urk... Owowow!! I just smacked my\nhip on something!\nWell, not my hip... My...whatever it\nis I have now... My brim? Whatever!\n"
    .string "That old fool must just love sending\npeople on dangerous missions!\nAnd how did that {COLOR}{RED}Librari{COLOR}{WHITE} get into\nthe {COLOR}{RED}Temple of Droplets{COLOR}{WHITE}, anyway?\nI guess the answer lies up ahead.\nKeep moving, boy!${UNK_030091}Brrr...chatter chatter...\n"
    .string "I'm freezing in here...!!\nIf you don't find that {COLOR}{GREEN}element {COLOR}{WHITE}quickly,\nI'm going to turn into a hatsicle!!\n{UNK_030092}Hurry up, {PLAYER}!\n${UNK_030091}It may be the Royal Crypt, but graves\nare creepy, no matter whose they are!\nWhere are we supposed to go to meet\nthis {COLOR}{RED}King Gustaf{COLOR}{WHITE} anyway?\nI'm not so sure I even want to anymore!\nCan we just go somewhere less creepy?$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}What an irritation! We find our way to\nthe very tops of the clouds...\nAnd now we have to go even higher\nto find a floating palace?\nI can't believe what a long way we've\ncome. And look how high we are!\nDon't look down, {PLAYER}! And watch\nyour step! It's a long fall from here!${UNK_030091}How much farther do we have to go!?\nThis place goes on forever!\nAh, there's no point in complaining\nabout it. We must press onward!\nAfter all, how much more could there\nbe? Come on, {PLAYER}! Let's go!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Whoa...!\n\nIs this really {COLOR}{RED}Hyrule Castle{COLOR}{WHITE}? I can't\nbelieve it! What's happened here?\n{COLOR}{RED}Vaati{COLOR}{WHITE}'s magic has grown more\npowerful than I'd imagined...\n{UNK_030092}But the {COLOR}{RED}king{COLOR}{WHITE} and {COLOR}{RED}Zelda{COLOR}{WHITE} are in danger,\n"
    .string "{PLAYER}! Let's go!${UNK_030092}These raindrops are like boulders of\nwater to us, kid! Watch out!\nIf one of them hits us, it'll sting\nsomething fierce!${UNK_030091}Hehehe! So, what do you think,\n{PLAYER}?\n{UNK_010A}Pretty dark and spooky, isn't it?\nMakes you wanna cry, doesn't it?\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}What? You're...not scared?\nWell, good! Neither am I!\n{UNK_030091}So, um... Come on, let's go...${UNK_030092}Wow! Look at the size of that waterfall!\nBeautiful! Simply beautiful, my boy!${UNK_030092}A stone door!\n\nSo! This was what they meant by all of\nthat {QT}{COLOR}{RED}source of the flow{COLOR}{WHITE}{QT} business!\nWell, this waterfall certainly is the\nsource of all Hyrule's water.\n"
    .string "According to {COLOR}{RED}King Gustaf{COLOR}{WHITE}, the"
    .string " final\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{GREEN}element {COLOR}{WHITE}lies somewhere behind the falls.\n"
    .string "We've dawdled long enough, {PLAYER}!\n"
    .string "Let's go find that element!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}What have we here? Some kind\n"
    .string "of vortex?\n"
    .string "Well, we seem to have hit a dead end...\n"
    .string "What shall we do from here?$"
    .string "{UNK_010A}... ...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}Am I still alive?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{UNK_010A}... ...\n"
    .string "... ...\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}{UNK_03008D}{PLAYER}!!\n"
    .string "What were you thinking, child!\n"
    .string "You just reaped the whirlwind, as\n"
    .string "they say! We could be dead right now!\n"
    .string "{UNK_010A}... ...\n"
    .string "... ...\n"
    .string "...{UNK_0101}But I must admit, it did the trick!{UNK_03008E}\n"
    .string "Are we...in the land above the clouds?\n"
    .string "Then {COLOR}{YELLOW}there must be something{COLOR}{WHITE} here that\n"
    .string "can lead us to the final {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "Let's go find it!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}Now how do you build something\n"
    .string "like this on top of a cloud?\n"
    .string "Maybe someone lives insi"
    .string "de. If so,\n"
    .string "perhaps we could ask for the {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE}?\n"
    .string "It's worth a shot, {PLAYER}!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}So this perfectly normal-looking stone\n"
    .string "was another {COLOR}{YELLOW}portal{COLOR}{WHITE} to the Minish world!\n"
    .string "There may be other {COLOR}{YELLOW}rock portals{COLOR}{WHITE}. Keep\n"
    .string "your eyes peeled, boy...$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}That's right! Even some human objects\n"
    .string "are {COLOR}{YELLOW}portals{COLOR}{WHITE} to the Minish world!\n"
    .string "Those Minish may not look like much,\n"
    .string "but they are quite crafty!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}What? ...What is this?\n"
    .string "What's happened here!?\n"
    .string "They've been turned to stone! All of\n"
    .string "them! The minister...and the guards!\n"
    .string "Everyone in the castle, all just\n"
    .string "like {COLOR}{RED}Princess Zelda{COLOR}{WHITE}...\n"
    .string "This can only be the work of that evil\n"
    .string "Vaati! What cruelty. {PLAYER}!\n"
    .string "We must use the power of the sacred\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{GREEN}Four Sword{COLOR}{WHITE} to {COLOR}{YELLOW}undo this evil{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Once you've pulled off their {COLOR}{YELLOW}iron masks{COLOR}{WHITE},\n"
    .string "those guys are no trouble whatsoever.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Your sword won't make a dent in their\n"
    .string "thorny armor!\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{YELLOW}Flip them over{COLOR}{WHITE} before you strike!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Don't panic, {PLAYER}! {COLOR}{YELLOW}Only one of\n"
    .string "them is real!{COLOR}{WHITE} The rest are fakes!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}With their {COLOR}{YELLOW}stone masks{COLOR}{WHITE} on, these\n"
    .string "things can put up quite a fight.\n"
    .string "If you just unmask them, though, they\n"
    .string "won't pose much of a threat.$"
    .string "{UNK_041000}Hmn?! Hmmmmnnnn...\n"
    .string "Ah, of course! How silly of me!{UNK_030092}\n"
    .string "Hey, my boy! {COLOR}{YELLOW}Jump into that whirlwind{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "over there for me!\n"
    .string "Heh heh heh... I wonder, is this a\n"
    .string "great idea or a terrible one?$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Whoa! How about that?! Of all the\n"
    .string "places for them to hide a portal!\n"
    .string "You've done well, my boy. Was that\n"
    .string "intuition? Or...just a lucky guess?{UNK_030090}$"
    .string "{UNK_030090}Hmn? There's something fishy about\n"
    .string "this area...\n"
    .string "I can't say exactly what, though...\n"
    .string "Just something weird in general...\n"
    .string "Don't you feel it?$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Whoa! So there WAS a portal\n"
    .string "hidden there!\n"
    .string "I knew I sensed something!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}So, this must be {COLOR}{RED}Castor Wilds{COLOR}{WHITE}...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "It's a nasty, dank place, filled with\n"
    .string "swampland and mire...\n"
    .string "But we know there's an {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE} waiting\n"
    .string "for us somewhere in here, so...\n"
    .string "In we go! Come on, {PLAYER}!\n"
    .string "Into the muck with us!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Now, that is one nasty-looking statue!\n"
    .string "That {COLOR}{YELLOW}eye{COLOR}{WHITE} has such an evil glower to it.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}There's only one thing to do here. Just\n"
    .string "break those pots that are in the way!\n"
    .string "Stand in front of them and press {RIGHT}\n"
    .string "to {COLOR}{YELLOW}lift them over your head{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "Then press it again to {COLOR}{YELLOW}throw them{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}With this {COLOR}{GREEN}small key{COLOR}{WHITE}, we should be able\n"
    .string "to open any locked door "
    .string "here!\n"
    .string "But I should warn you, {COLOR}{YELLOW}once you've\n"
    .string "used the key{COLOR}{WHITE}, {COLOR}{YELLOW}it will vanish{COLOR}{WHITE} forever.\n"
    .string "To use it, just stand in front of\n"
    .string "a locked door and press {RIGHT}.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Do you see that lever? I think you\n"
    .string "should be able to {COLOR}{YELLOW}pull it{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "Just stand in front of it and press {RIGHT}\n"
    .string "to grab it, then press {UNK_BUTTON} to pull.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Once you take hold of something with\n"
    .string "{RIGHT}, use {DPAD} to {COLOR}{YELLOW}push{COLOR}{WHITE} or {COLOR}{YELLOW}pull{COLOR}{WHITE} it.\n"
    .string "This is extremely important, so I hope\n"
    .string "you take pains to r"
    .string "emember it!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Wow! Look at the size of that barrel!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Hm? Oh, right! Right! How silly of me!\n"
    .string "It's not big{SYM_UNK} {COLOR}{YELLOW}we're just small{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Wha--!? Hey, be careful, my lad!\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{YELLOW}The barrel just moved{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}What we need now is something to\n"
    .string "hold down this switch...$"
    .string "{UNK_030090}Now what?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Unless we find a way to travel by\n"
    .string "water, we won't be going much farther.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}This must be what the humans who built\n"
    .string "this mine used to get around in here.\n"
    .string "Maybe we should hop in.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Hm? What? After all this, you don't\n"
    .string "expect me to believe you're scared!\n"
    .string "There's nothing to be afraid of here!\n"
    .string "Come on, let's go!$"
    .string "{UNK_030093}Sweet jumping jellyfish, that was awful!\n"
    .string "Hey, kid, what are you smiling about?\n"
    .string "I knew it was madness to risk our lives\n"
    .string "in that rickety human contraption!\n"
    .string "From now on, let's just stick to our\n"
    .string "feet! Well, I mean...your feet.$"
    .string "{UNK_030091}Oh my! It looks really, REALLY\n"
    .string "hot in that lava!\n"
    .string "Trust me: falling into that would\n"
    .string "be a bad idea. I'm sure you agree.$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}How interesting! So there was a {COLOR}{YELLOW}portal{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "hidden away in here, hm?\n"
    .string "Whenever you want me to shrink you\n"
    .string "down, just hop up here and press {RIGHT}!$"
    .string "{UNK_030090}Phew...! We barely made it! I was\n"
    .string "certain we'd run out of time!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Hmn?! Did something just fall down,\n"
    .string "or was it just my imagination?$"
    .string "{UNK_030091}What?! This floor is made out of ice!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Be careful not to fall and freeze\n"
    .string "your backside to the floor, {PLAYER}!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Hm. It looks like something is frozen\n"
    .string "inside this block of ice...\n"
    .string "{PLAYER}, why don't you go take a\n"
    .string "look?$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Hey! The sunlight's shining through!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Ahhh... It's so nice and warm. I can\n"
    .string "feel myself starting to defrost again.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}{UNK_041000}Hey...!!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Well done, {PLAYER}!\n"
    .string "This looks to be the {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE}, all right.\n"
    .string "But what will we do?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "We can't even touch it while it's\n"
    .string "trapped in that ice...\n"
    .string "We'll need to melt it off somehow...$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Of course! Sunlight! Once we get some\n"
    .string "sunlight in to melt the ice,\n"
    .string "that {COLOR}{GREEN}element {COLOR}{WHITE}will be as good as ours!\n"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}We did it, {PLAYER}!\n"
    .string "Now we can take the {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "That was a lot of trouble,\n"
    .string "but we finally did it, and...\n"
    .string "What in blazes!?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Hey, something's not right here!!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}What!? What's this?!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "That stupid Octorok stole our {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Don't just stand there! We've got to go\n"
    .string "get it! {PLAYER}! Now!$"
    .string "{UNK_030091}{PLAYER}! Where are you?\n"
    .string "Are you still there under me?\n"
    .string "It's so dark, I can't see my beak\n"
    .string "in front of my face!\n"
    .string "Watch your step! I don't want you\n"
    .string "to trip over anything...$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Oh my! There was a portal hidden\n"
    .string "in there?$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}There's a fluffy cloud floating here.\n"
    .string "It looks awfully comfortable.$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}That panel... I think if we stomped on\n"
    .string "it hard enough, it might flip over...$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}There's a strong gale blowing here!\n"
    .string "Try not to get swept away!\n"
    .string "And hold on to your hat!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Perhaps your sword could reflect the\n"
    .string "blasts coming from those statues.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}What in the world is that?!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}Hmmm... Yes, yes... It certainly\n"
    .string "does look suspicious...$"
    .string "{UNK_030091}Huh? Wha--? What in the world!?$"
    .string "{UNK_03008F}My word! It's a treasure chest!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008F}There seems to be a switch here!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008F}Oh, a {COLOR}{GREEN}Piece of Heart{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "Well, that IS useful.$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}So this is your house...\n"
    .string "Well, it seems like a nice place.\n"
    .string "...So, where's my room?$"
    .string "{UNK_030090}So! This is your room? That makes it\n"
    .string "my room, too, right?$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}I sense something unusual here...\n"
    .string "Is it something hidden?\n"
    .string "I won't tell anyone, so come on!\n"
    .string "Show me!$"
    .string "{UNK_030090}Why, this is the shopkeeper\n"
    .string "Stockwell's house!\n"
    .string "You can tell much about a person\n"
    .string "from the house he keeps, hm?\n"
    .string "It's pretty unusual, even by Hyrulean\n"
    .string "standards. It even has a pool!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}That mustachioed guy strikes me as\n"
    .string "somewhat unreliable.\n"
    .string "There's something fishy about this\n"
    .string "room, too.$"
    .string "{UNK_030090}Sniff sniff sniff! Mmmm, doesn't that\n"
    .string "smell spectacular?\n"
    .string "Perhaps they give out free samples.\n"
    .string "I say, would you...ask for me?$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}There seem to be many interesting\n"
    .string "books in here...\n"
    .string "  {COLOR}{YELLOW}Hyrule on 10 Rupees a Day{COLOR}{WHITE},\n"
    .string "  {COLOR}{YELLOW}So Your Son Wants to Be a Hero{COLOR}{WHITE}...\n"
    .string "  {COLOR}{YELLOW}It Could Be Verse!{COLOR}{WHITE}, by Percy, and\n"
    .string "  {COLOR}{YELLOW}Rem's Anthology for Sleepless Nights{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "Hmmm, they all look pretty good,\n"
    .string "but which one to read first?$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Are you sure I look all right? I never\n"
    .string "know what to wear to formal occasions.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}How tranquil...\n"
    .string "And those cows look so...delicious.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Whoa! Did you see that cat looking\n"
    .string "at me?! I know it wants a piece of me!$"
    .string "{UNK_030091}Waaah! That really startled me!\n"
    .string "Everything's scary when you're small!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Hm? Whoa! It...blew up?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Hey, kid! Look at where that stone\n"
    .string "marker used to be...\n"
    .string "There's some strange {COLOR}{YELLOW}symbol {COLOR}{WHITE}on the\n"
    .string "ground.\n"
    .string "Yes, of course{UNK_010A}... Why, this must be...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}...Well, I haven't the foggiest, to be\n"
    .string "honest. Hm...$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Hey! That stone marker crumbled! And\n"
    .string "there's another of those {COLOR}{YELLOW}symbols{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "...You know, no matter how many times\n"
    .string "I see that happen, it still rattles me.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Hey! We've found another {COLOR}{YELLOW}Wind Crest{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Now we have one more point of travel\n"
    .string "when we use the {COLOR}{GREEN}Ocarina of Wind{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}Aha!! So that mysterious mark we've\n"
    .string "been seeing is a {COLOR}{YELLOW}Wind Crest{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "If you play the {COLOR}{GREEN}Ocarina of Wind{COLOR}{WHITE}, Zeffa\n"
    .string "comes to pick you up and fly you away.\n"
    .string "That means we can have Zeffa carry us\n"
    .string "to any other {COLOR}{YELLOW}Wind Crest{COLOR}{WHITE} we've seen.\n"
    .string "Are you following me, {PLAYER}?\n"
    .string "Don't hurt your brain thinking about it.\n"
    .string "Just give it a try, and you'll see what\n"
    .string "I'm talking about.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Hmn?!\n"
    .string "Say, look at that, {PLAYER}!\n"
    .string "There's a {COLOR}{GREEN}book {COLOR}{WHITE}up on top of the\n"
    .string "bookcase!\n"
    .string "But how are we going to get it? We\n"
    .string "can't reach it, and we have no ladder.\n"
    .string "And I don't think just shaking the\n"
    .string "bookcase will make it fall, either.\n"
    .string "This presents an interesting\n"
    .string "problem, wouldn't you say?$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Hey now! You can't just go waltzing\n"
    .string "into people's homes like that!\n"
    .string "If the owner isn't home, you'll just\n"
    .string "have to come back later.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Hm. This house appears to be empty...\n"
    .string "Maybe we shouldn't go in here.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Hm? That's unfortunate...\n"
    .string "They're not open yet.\n"
    .string "Ah, well. We'll just have to come\n"
    .string "back later, won't we?$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}The door is shut.\n"
    .string "We can't open it from this side{UNK_010A}...$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Hey, you don't have any {COLOR}{GREEN}Kinstone\n"
    .string "pieces{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "How can you fuse Kinstones if you\n"
    .string "don't have any Kinstone pieces!?$"
    .string "{UNK_030090}I don't think we can walk fast enough\n"
    .string "to cross this swamp.\n"
    .string "We're going to have to find some way\n"
    .string "to get across safely...$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Hey, kid! Why don't you take that {COLOR}{GREEN}Cane\n"
    .string "of Pacci{COLOR}{WHITE} and fire it at that hole?\n"
    .string "I mean, you never know what'll happen\n"
    .string "until you try, right?$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_030091}Oooooog. I'm sure I've mentioned this\n"
    .string "before, but I'm no good with heights.\n"
    .string "Wait, hold on... I think I see\n"
    .string "something down there!\n"
    .string "Sigh... I guess that means we have to\n"
    .string "take the plunge after all, hm?$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Hmph! There's a {COLOR}{GREEN}locked{COLOR}{WHITE} door here! See if\n"
    .string "you can find a key to open it.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}That noise just now! What was that?\n"
    .string "Something must have happened...\n"
    .string "Be careful, {PLAYER}!!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}Hmm! Yes, yes, yes! Why, it all makes\n"
    .string "sense now, doesn't it, boy?\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}Librari{COLOR}{WHITE} used these {COLOR}{GREEN}flippers {COLOR}{WHITE}to swim to\n"
    .string "the entrance to the {COLOR}{RED}Temple of Droplets{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "So, if you put these on, you should be\n"
    .string "able to swim, too! Remarkable!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}If I recall correctly, and I guarantee\n"
    .string "that I do, my boy...\n"
    .string "I think Syrup said to stand in front of\n"
    .string "a sleeping person and press {RIGHT}.$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}Now there's a puzzler...{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}I suspect there's not much more we can\n"
    .string "do here right now. Let's press on.\n"
    .string "Perhaps we can work this from another\n"
    .string "angle later on.$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}That hand is a real pain, {PLAYER}.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Perhaps one of those gizmos you carry\n"
    .string "around can do something to it!$"
