    .string "What!? I haven't even had time to\n"
    .string "settle in, and you're bothering me?\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}Deepwood Shrine{COLOR}{WHITE} lies, obviously enough,\n"
    .string "deep in the heart of these woods!\n"
    .string "So says my superior intuitive sense.\n"
    .string "{UNK_0105}Now, get a move on!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}This place is dangerous...\n"
    .string "There are so many monsters.\n"
    .string "{UNK_0106}Kid! Be careful!\n"
    .string "{UNK_0105}You wouldn't want to let them hurt me!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}{QT}Check your surroundings to make\n"
    .string "sure there's nothing hidden!{QT}\n"
    .string "That's the cardinal rule of\n"
    .string "adventuring! {UNK_0107}So don't you forget it!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Sometimes, a way will open for you\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{YELLOW}when you are smaller{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "You've got to try everything\n"
    .string "you can, my boy!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}The {COLOR}{RED}Minish {COLOR}{WHITE}are exceptionally tiny!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "That means, when you're their size,\n"
    .string "you can fit into some {COLOR}{YELLOW}pretty tiny spots{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "That includes places you couldn't\n"
    .string "go at your normal size.\n"
    .string "That's a pretty good tip, huh?$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Hey, kid! Maybe now you'll have a little\n"
    .string "respect for me, huh?\n"
    .string "That's right! I can turn you tiny\n"
    .string "anytime you want!\n"
    .string "{UNK_010A}Well, that is, if there's a stump{UNK_0101} or\n"
    .string "some other kind of {COLOR}{YELLOW}portal{COLOR}{WHITE} nearby...$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}Hm. We're not going to get anywhere\n"
    .string "if the Minish can't understand you{UNK_010A}...$"
    .string "{UNK_030090}The {COLOR}{RED}Minish {COLOR}{WHITE}certainly do seem to be\n"
    .string "curious about the ways of humans...$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}{QT}Don't ponder{SYM_UNK} wander!{QT}\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Don't waste your time trying to\n"
    .string "think things through too quickly.\n"
    .string "Take your time! Look around {COLOR}{RED}Minish\n"
    .string "Village{COLOR}{WHITE} and see what you can see!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}A strange nut that will allow us to\n"
    .string "understand the Minish language{UNK_010A}...\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}The {COLOR}{GREEN}Jingle Nut{COLOR}{WHITE}, did he say...?\n"
    .string "No, wait... That's not it...\n"
    .string "Ah, I remember now! It was the\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{GREEN}Jabber Nut{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "That's what it was... Come on, my boy!\n"
    .string "We've got to find the {COLOR}{GREEN}Jabber Nut{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}So that {COLOR}{GREEN}Jabber Nut{COLOR}{WHITE} was, uhh...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Yeah, the {COLOR}{RED}Minish with\n"
    .string "glasses{COLOR}{WHITE} said,{UNK_010A} um...\n"
    .string "Was his name Feltari?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}Anyway, we're supposed to go south\n"
    .string "until we find a house {COLOR}{YELLOW}inside a barrel{COLOR}{WHITE}.$"
    .string "Once you've learned how to speak\n"
    .string "the Minish language,\n"
    .string "we'll be able to ask about the\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{GREEN}sacred blade{COLOR}{WHITE}. {UNK_03008D}Let's get to it!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}Well? What are you waiting for? You\n"
    .string "can understand their language, right?\n"
    .string "So stop wasting time and find out\n"
    .string "about that sacred blade!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}So only the {COLOR}{RED}Minish {COLOR}{WHITE}can repair\n"
    .string "the {COLOR}{GREEN}sword{COLOR}{WHITE}, hm?\n"
    .string "Maybe we should find out what the\n"
    .string "other {COLOR}{RED}Minish {COLOR}{WHITE}know about that.$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}You've never actually seen the\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}Minish {COLOR}{WHITE}before, have you?\n"
    .string "Ah, well, they are mostly good\n"
    .string "folk. Yes{UNK_010A}...mostly...$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}If you have any hopes of reforging the\n"
    .string "sacred blade, do as the elder says.\n"
    .string "Go find the {COLOR}{GREEN}Earth Element{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}A Minish shrine filled with monsters?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}It sounds dangerous in there!{UNK_010A} We'd\n"
    .string "better be careful...\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}I mean, you'd better be careful!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}What? Don't tell me you're lost!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Listen, if you get lost, just {COLOR}{YELLOW}examine\n"
    .string "your surroundings{COLOR}{WHITE} closely...\n"
    .string "I'm sure you can find some kind\n"
    .string "of clue nearby.$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}We got through that monster-filled\n"
    .string "shrine and found the {COLOR}{GREEN}Earth Element{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Great work, kid! You're doing a fine\n"
    .string "job! Thanks to my help, of course.$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}The Minish elder wanted us to speak\n"
    .string "with him once we found that {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "That's where we ought to go.$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}{UNK_010A}We need to learn how to reforge\n"
    .string "the broken {COLOR}{GREEN}sacred blade{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}{COLOR}{RED}We'll have to speak with the Minish\n"
    .string "elder {COLOR}{WHITE}about that, won't we?\n"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Well? What are you waiting for!? Evil\n"
    .string "won't go vanquishing itself, you know!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}So we're supposed to meet a Minish\n"
    .string "blacksmith named {COLOR}{RED}Melari{COLOR}{WHITE} on {COLOR}{RED}Mt. Crenel{COLOR}{WHITE}?\n"
    .string "You know, maybe we should stop in at\n"
    .string "the town of Hyrule before leaving...$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}What's the matter? Are you lost?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Just where do you think you're\n"
    .string "taking us, anyway?\n"
    .string "Look at a {COLOR}{GREEN}map {COLOR}{WHITE}or something! Just\n"
    .string "press START to see it.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Have you ever visited Hyrule before?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "What? You have?\n"
    .string "...What's it like?\n"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Not that I... I mean, I've seen it\n"
    .string "before! Of course I have!\n"
    .string "I'm very well traveled. I just wanted\n"
    .string "to see...what you thought of it!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}{COLOR}{RED}Mount Crenel{COLOR}{WHITE} is a forbidding and\n"
    .string "rocky place with many steep cliffs.\n"
    .string "It lies just west of {COLOR}{RED}Hyrule Town{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "We ought to equip ourselves in town\n"
    .string "before risking the journey.$"
    .string "{UNK_030091}Aww...{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}I guess the festival that was going on\n"
    .string "here in town has already ended.\n"
    .string "I really wanted to see that...{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{UNK_030092}It must have looked quite different\n"
    .string "when the festival was going on, hm?$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Look at all these shops! This is so\n"
    .string "different from {COLOR}{RED}Minish Village{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "I-I-I... I can't decide where to\n"
    .string "go next!\n"
    .string "Come on, my boy! Let's go shopping!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Oh, don't tell me you've forgotten\n"
    .string "already! What is WRONG with you?\n"
    .string "The Minish elder told us to see {COLOR}{RED}Melari{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "up on {COLOR}{RED}Mount Crenel{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "{UNK_030090}But how do you suppose we're going to\n"
    .string "climb that pile of rocks, anyway?{UNK_010A}$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}Hmmm...{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}If the mountain is anything like those\n"
    .string "woods, there will be monsters ahead.\n"
    .string "{UNK_030090}I'm not really busting a seam to see\n"
    .string "this {COLOR}{RED}Melari{COLOR}{WHITE}, but...we have no choice.{UNK_010A}$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Oh, hey! I totally forgot!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "That sword technique you learned from\n"
    .string "the swordsman...\n"
    .string "The {COLOR}{GREEN}Spin Attack{COLOR}{WHITE}, that's what it's\n"
    .string "called, right? That is so incredible!\n"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Do you think you could teach\n"
    .string "it to me sometime?\n"
    .string "Hm?! Hey! Don't give me that look!\n"
    .string "I can do anything that you can do!\n"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Just give me some arms, and I'll\n"
    .string "show you what's what!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}A {COLOR}{YELLOW}bean{COLOR}{WHITE} that {COLOR}{YELLOW}grow"
    .string "s{COLOR}{WHITE} when you {COLOR}{YELLOW}pour water\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{WHITE}on it{UNK_010A}...\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}I guess it was a good idea to buy that\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{GREEN}bottle{COLOR}{WHITE} from the Deku Scrub after all!\n"
    .string "{UNK_030092}See, my boy? Listen to me,\n"
    .string "and you'll go far!$"
    .string "{UNK_030090}Hrm... Where on {COLOR}{RED}Mount Crenel {COLOR}{WHITE}is this\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}Melari {COLOR}{WHITE}the blacksmith, anyway?\n"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Well, we know he's Minish, so try\n"
    .string "to keep your eyes peeled!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Hey, kid! What's the matter?\n"
    .string "You don't know which way to go?\n"
    .string "At times like these, try everything you\n"
    .string "can at spots that {COLOR}{YELLOW}seem like dead ends{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "Sometimes, you can find a way hidden in\n"
    .string "the most unlikely of spots!\n"
    .string "...Um, sometimes.$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}Hmm... It seems there are {COLOR}{YELLOW}two types of\n"
    .string "bean{COLOR}{WHITE} on Mount Crenel: blue and green.{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}If the color is different, I suppose how\n"
    .string "you treat each one is different, too.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Remember, we have to find our way to\n"
    .string "the top of {COLOR}{RED}Mount Crenel{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "Once we're there, we'll start looking\n"
    .string "for that {COLOR}{RED}Melari{COLOR}{WHITE}.$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Explain something to me, my boy...\n"
    .string "Why are we just wandering around?\n"
    .string "We're supposed to be scaling {COLOR}{RED}Mount\n"
    .string "Crenel{COLOR}{WHITE} and looking for {COLOR}{RED}Melari{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Somewhere on {COLOR}{RED}Mount Crenel{COLOR}{WHITE}, there's\n"
    .string "a Minish blacksmith named {COLOR}{RED}Melari{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "We have to find him!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}There are some strange creatures on\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}Mount Crenel{COLOR}{WHITE}...\n"
    .string "Creatures I've never seen before, and\n"
    .string "your sword alone won't beat them!\n"
    .string "Don't give up hope, though! Try your\n"
    .string "other {COLOR}{GREEN}items{COLOR}{WHITE} on them!\n"
    .string "Well...you don't need me to tell you\n"
    .string "how to do your job.\n"
    .string "Just deal with those monsters, and\n"
    .string "I'll take care of everything else.{UNK_010A}$"
    .string "{UNK_030091}What?\n"
    .string "You're lost again, aren't you?\n"
    .string "Have you bothered reading any of\n"
    .string "those {COLOR}{YELLOW}signs{COLOR}{WHITE} we've been seeing?\n"
    .string "You really ought to study them. They\n"
    .string "might have some useful information!\n"
    .string "...Not that I've been reading them\n"
    .string "either...$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Hey! Hurry up and find that {COLOR}{RED}Melari{COLOR}{WHITE},\n"
    .string "so we can fix the sacred blade!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}Have you noticed something odd about\n"
    .string "the {COLOR}{RED}Mountain Minish{COLOR}{WHITE}?\n"
    .string "They're just a little different from\n"
    .string "the Forest Minish, aren't they?\n"
    .string "There seem to be many kinds of Minish,\n"
    .string "just as there are many kinds of human.\n"
    .string "And...many kinds of hat, too.\n"
    .string "Mustn't forget the hats.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}These Mountain {COLOR}{RED}Minish {COLOR}{WHITE}sure are\n"
    .string "hard workers!\n"
    .string "We should work just as hard and sing\n"
    .string "a spiffy little song, like they do!\n"
    .string "What do you think? Hey! Kid...?\n"
    .string "Are you still listening to me?$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}This isn't the time to idle about,\n"
    .string "you lazy boy!\n"
    .string "We have to go search for the {COLOR}{GREEN}elements{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "while Melari works on that sword!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}So humans made this mine long ago?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Well it's full of monsters now,\n"
    .string "kid, so watch your back!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}Perhaps the humans who made this mine\n"
    .string "will have left some things we can use...{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}After all, there's no reason to let\n"
    .string "good wares go to waste.$"
    .string "{UNK_030090}So we beat the fire monster and got\n"
    .string "the second {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE}! Incredible!{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}Kid, you may just be some kind of\n"
    .string "hero or something!\n"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}I knew I sensed potential in you!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Oh, so I bet {COLOR}{RED}Melari {COLOR}{WHITE}has finished with\n"
    .string "that {COLOR}{GREEN}sword{COLOR}{WHITE}. We should go pick it up!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}So how about that sword that {COLOR}{RED}Melari{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "fixed up for you, huh?\n"
    .string "I may be just a hat, but I can admire\n"
    .string "good craftsmanship!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}We must find the {COLOR}{RED}elemental sanctuary{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "to fill the sword with elemental power.\n"
    .string "I'd never have looked for the {COLOR}{RED}elemental\n"
    .string "sanctuary{COLOR}{WHITE} in {COLOR}{RED}Hyrule Castle{COLOR}{WHITE}, though!{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}You know how to get there, right?\n"
    .string "Let's go!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}So of the four {COLOR}{GREEN}elements{COLOR}{WHITE}, we've got\n"
    .string "Earth and Fire...\n"
    .string "And now, we have the {COLOR}{GREEN}White Sword{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "to absorb their power!\n"
    .string "That means the sacred blade's power\n"
    .string "has almost been restored!$"
    .string "{UNK_030091}Why do you look so confused? Don't you\n"
    .string "understand what's going on?{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}The {COLOR}{RED}elemental sanctuary {COLOR}{WHITE}exists between\n"
    .string "the human world and the Minish world.\n"
    .string "Here, let me explain with a little\n"
    .string "example: in a ham sandwich...\n"
    .string "the elemental sanctuary would be the\n"
    .string "ham between the two slices of bread!\n"
    .string "...You've still got that look.\n"
    .string "Did I just make it more confusing?$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}So! We must infuse the {COLOR}{GREEN}White Sword{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "with the {COLOR}{GREEN}elemental power{COLOR}{WHITE}.{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}That means we must find the\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}elemental sanctuary{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "And the way we do that is... Um...\n"
    .string "Well, I'm sure we'll figure it out!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}I think that you and I may be the only\n"
    .string "ones who can see the mystic doorway...\n"
    .string "Well, that's fine by me. That means\n"
    .string "no one will notice anything unusual!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}We just need to infuse the {COLOR}{GREEN}sword{COLOR}{WHITE} with\n"
    .string "the power of these two {COLOR}{GREEN}elements{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "Then, the sacred blade will be\n"
    .string "nearly complete!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Only two {COLOR}{GREEN}elements{COLOR}{WHITE} remain!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "They must be in the places marked on\n"
    .string "your {COLOR}{GREEN}map{COLOR}{WHITE} by the Minish elder!\n"
    .string "Why don't we take another look at that\n"
    .string "map? If memory serves me correctly...{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}There should be a mark out on the\n"
    .string "westernmost edge of {COLOR}{RED}Castor Wilds{COLOR}{WHITE}.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}So the {COLOR}{GREEN}sacred blade{COLOR}{WHITE} has finally started\n"
    .string "to show us a portion of its power!\n"
    .string "If we use this new skill of yours well,\n"
    .string "we should be able to access new areas!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}If you're after the {COLOR}{GREEN}elements{COLOR}{WHITE}, just\n"
    .string "check your {COLOR}{GREEN}map{COLOR}{WHITE} by pressing START.\n"
    .string "I believe the elder of the Forest\n"
    .string "Minish marked the locations there.$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}Hrm... According to the map, we'll need\n"
    .string "to cross {COLOR}{RED}Castor Wilds{COLOR}{WHITE}.{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "That unexplored region is where we\n"
    .string "must go to find the next {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE}!{UNK_0101}$"
    .string "{UNK_030090}The swamp covering {COLOR}{RED}Castor Wilds{COLOR}{WHITE} looks\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{YELLOW}impassable on foot{COLOR}{WHITE}. What will we do!?{UNK_010A}$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}{PLAYER}, how long has it been since\n"
    .string "you left home?\n"
    .string "Your grandfather must be worried.\n"
    .string "Why don't you show your face at home?\n"
    .string "He must have plenty of news to share\n"
    .string "with you by now.$"
    .string "{UNK_030090}Hnyaaaawn...{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}Mmmmnumumummm...\n"
    .string "Even I'm getting tired now...{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "I guess I need a {COLOR}{GREEN}wake-up mushroom{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "or something to perk me up!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Hoho! Well...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}The big lake spreading out to the west\n"
    .string "of Hyrule is {COLOR}{RED}Lake Hylia{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "The rich water that flows from it has\n"
    .string "fed the {COLOR}{RED}Minish Woods{COLOR}{WHITE} for millennia.\n"
    .string "Every day, you learn something new,\n"
    .string "don't you, {PLAYER}?$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}Well, I say! There seem to be a lot of\n"
    .string "Minish living in town, too...\n"
    .string "Even if they can't be seen, I'm sure the\n"
    .string "Minish make their presence known...$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}So, about that {COLOR}{GREEN}wake-up mushroom{COLOR}{WHITE} you\n"
    .string "just bought... It kind of, um...smells.\n"
    .string "COUGH! COUGH!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{UNK_030091}I suppose that awful stink could pull\n"
    .string "anyone from the deepest slumber!$"
    .string "{UNK_030090}Hey, {PLAYER}. I've been up here for\n"
    .string "a while, and I've been wondering...\n"
    .string "I know about hats now, but I don't\n"
    .string "know much about Hyrulean shoes...\n"
    .string "Where could we go to learn a little\n"
    .string "more about that?$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}So about that old lady in the woods\n"
    .string "named {COLOR}{RED}Syrup{COLOR}{WHITE} or something...\n"
    .string "Didn't she strike you as a little\n"
    .string "bit, well, strange?\n"
    .string "I'm confident that her {COLOR}{GREEN}potions{COLOR}{WHITE} work\n"
    .string "as advertised, though.\n"
    .string "She looks like someone who could whip\n"
    .string "up a mean magic brew...$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Once we cross {COLOR}{RED}Castor Wilds{COLOR}{WHITE}, the\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE} should be easy to find.\n"
    .string "If you forget where to go, just take\n"
    .string "a look at your {COLOR}{GREEN}map{COLOR}{WHITE}.$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}When you're crossing a swamp, you\n"
    .string "want to be as swift as the wind...\n"
    .string "There's no point in stopping to look\n"
    .string "around. Sightseeing is right out!\n"
    .string "What I'm trying to say is that I don't\n"
    .string "much relish the thought of a mud bath!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}That {COLOR}{YELLOW}one-eyed stone{COLOR}{WHITE} statue in {COLOR}{RED}Castor\n"
    .string "Wilds{COLOR}{WHITE} looks like it's staring at us!\n"
    .string "...That eye really creeps me out.$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}Creepy {COLOR}{RED}ruins{COLOR}{WHITE} standing on the far side\n"
    .string "of {COLOR}{RED}Castor Wilds{COLOR}{WHITE}...{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}Maybe that's where the ancient people\n"
    .string "who guarded the {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE} used to live.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}That {COLOR}{GREEN}element {COLOR}{WHITE}is sure to be protected by\n"
    .string "traps inside those ancient ruins!\n"
    .string "{PLAYER}, be careful!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Don't just wander around aimlessly...\n"
    .string "That's the quickest way to get lost!\n"
    .string "If you do get lost, look at your {COLOR}{GREEN}map{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "immediately to get your bearings.\n"
    .string "You will find your way only if you know\n"
    .string "where you are AND where you're going.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}The next {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE} is near {COLOR}{RED}Lake Hylia{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "Now, how are we going to get there?\n"
    .string "I wonder who might be able to help\n"
    .string "us out with something like that...$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}All we have to do is use the {COLOR}{GREEN}Ocarina of\n"
    .string "Wind{COLOR}{WHITE} to call Zeffa!\n"
    .string "If we stand on a {COLOR}{YELLOW}Wind Crest{COLOR}{WHITE} and call\n"
    .string "him, he'll take us where we want to go!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Well, now that we've got this {COLOR}{GREEN}Ocarina\n"
    .string "of Wind{COLOR}{WHITE}, shouldn't we try to use it?\n"
    .string "Even places we've seen before may hold\n"
    .string "new surprises if we try flying there...$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}Well, I'd never have suspected it of\n"
    .string "that {COLOR}{RED}Minish elder{COLOR}{WHITE} in the {COLOR}{RED}library{COLOR}{WHITE}...\n"
    .string "To think he was an adventurer! And\n"
    .string "that he visited the {COLOR}{RED}Temple of Droplets{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "Maybe we should look up that {COLOR}{RED}Librari{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "and hear what he has to say.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Hm. Now, how did {COLOR}{RED}Librari{COLOR}{WHITE} get into\n"
    .string "the {COLOR}{RED}Temple of Droplets{COLOR}{WHITE}?\n"
    .string "I guess we'll just have to go visit\n"
    .string "him at the library and ask.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}So, where in the library would any\n"
    .string "Minish folk live, anyway?\n"
    .string "Maybe those people who say the Minish\n"
    .string "exist {QT}{COLOR}{YELLOW}only in stories{COLOR}{WHITE}{QT} might be right!\n"
    .string "Hey! {PLAYER}! What's that look for?\n"
    .string "Don't tell me you were one of...them?\n"
    .string "You're kidding me! You're wearing a\n"
    .string "Minish person on your head, you oaf!\n"
    .string "I certainly hope you believe in us now!$"
    .string "{UNK_030091}How did we get roped into running all\n"
    .string "over creation returning library books?\n"
    .string "I understand it's all just to learn\n"
    .string "how to enter the {COLOR}{RED}Temple of Droplets{COLOR}{WHITE},\n"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}but this is hardly the sort of duty\n"
    .string "worthy of a great adventurer!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}Minish people are very interested in\n"
    .string "human ways.\n"
    .string "I think they watch the people in\n"
    .string "town very closely.\n"
    .string "They've probably been watching you,\n"
    .string "too, without your knowing it.\n"
    .string "Hey, {PLAYER}, careful what you say\n"
    .string "and do when you think you're alone!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}So there are three books that we're\n"
    .string "supposed to return, right?\n"
    .string "{PLAYER}, I'm sure you can handle it!\n"
    .string "Don't get me wrong! I'd love to help!\n"
    .string "But I'm a great Minish sage! I don't\n"
    .string "understand your big, human ways!\n"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}So...I'm counting on you!$"
    .string "{UNK_030091}This really is starting to take valuable\n"
    .string "time from our search for the {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "{UNK_030092}But buck up, kiddo! We're almost\n"
    .string "done, {PLAYER}!!!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}I just can't figure out how {COLOR}{RED}Librari{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "got into the {COLOR}{RED}Temple of Droplets{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "I'm going crazy with curiosity!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}You know, even these Minish living in\n"
    .string "the town still have their own troubles.\n"
    .string "I feel like I've learned a lot here.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}The {COLOR}{RED}Temple of Droplets{COLOR}{WHITE} holds the last of\n"
    .string "the {COLOR}{GREEN}elements{COLOR}{WHITE}, like the Minish elder said.\n"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}So let's brace ourselves and do this!\n"
    .string "Are you ready, {PLAYER}?!\n"
    .string "... ...{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}What?! What's that face for?\n"
    .string "You don't want to brace yourself?! All\n"
    .string "right, fine! No bracing! Let's just go!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Did you know the {COLOR}{GREEN}flippers{COLOR}{WHITE} Librari gave\n"
    .string "you let you {COLOR}{YELLOW}dive {COLOR}{WHITE}as well as {COLOR}{YELLOW}swim{COLOR}{WHITE}?\n"
    .string "They're good for avoiding things when\n"
    .string "you're in the water...\n"
    .string "And let's face it, if something hits you\n"
    .string "in the head while you're swimming...\n"
    .string "I'm going to be the one who gets\n"
    .string "the worst of it.\n"
    .string "So please, remember that. For my sake,\n"
    .string "{PLAYER}!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Don't just wander around aimlessly...\n"
    .string "That's the quickest way to get lost!\n"
    .string "If you do get lost, look at your {COLOR}{GREEN}map{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "immediately to get your bearings.\n"
    .string "You will find your way only if you know\n"
    .string "where you are AND where you're going.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}That phantom we saw earlier... He said\n"
    .string "he was {COLOR}{RED}an ancient king of Hyrule{COLOR}{WHITE}.{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}What else do we know? The {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE} was\n"
    .string "nowhere to be seen in the {COLOR}{RED}Wind Ruins{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "I guess we'll just have to go to\n"
    .string "the place marked on our {COLOR}{GREEN}map{COLOR}{WHITE}...\n"
    .string "But first, you should infuse your\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{GREEN}sword{COLOR}{WHITE} with that {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "We must head for the {COLOR}{RED}elemental\n"
    .string "sanctuary{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}It seems the king and the guards are\n"
    .string "not be able to see it...\n"
    .string "But the entrance to the {COLOR}{RED}elemental\n"
    .string "sanctuary {COLOR}{WHITE}MUST be inside {COLOR}{RED}Hyrule Castle{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}{PLAYER}! Aren't you forgetting\n"
    .string "a little something?\n"
    .string "We need to infuse your {COLOR}{GREEN}sword{COLOR}{WHITE} with the\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{GREEN}element {COLOR}{WHITE}that we worked so hard to get!\n"
    .string "After all, we certainly worked hard\n"
    .string "enough to get it. We ought to use it!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}I suppose we'll have to try going\n"
    .string "to the point marked on the {COLOR}{GREEN}map{COLOR}{WHITE}...\n"
    .string "We have no other clues leading us to\n"
    .string "the remaining {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE}, that's for sure.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}{PLAYER}, there's only one\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE} remaining!\n"
    .string "Once you've used the {COLOR}{GREEN}sacred blade{COLOR}{WHITE} to\n"
    .string "free Princess Zelda from her curse,\n"
    .string "perhaps you can ask her out on\n"
    .string "a date or something.\n"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Don't worry, I'll be right there with you!\n"
    .string "You will need my advice, after all!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}Did you see that?\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}King Gustaf{COLOR}{WHITE} was calling us...{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}Perhaps we ought to visit the point\n"
    .string "marked on our {COLOR}{GREEN}map{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "It may have been a dream, but I'm sure\n"
    .string "it will make sense if we go there.$"
    .string "{UNK_030091}Uhh... Don't tell me the new path leads\n"
    .string "us {COLOR}{RED}into a grave{COLOR}{WHITE}...?{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}That means {COLOR}{RED}King Gustaf{COLOR}{WHITE} must really\n"
    .string "have been a...a...\n"
    .string "{UNK_030090}Whoa! I just got a chill down my seam!$"
    .string "{UNK_030090}I haven't mentioned it up to now, but\n"
    .string "ghosts and stuff like that...{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}{UNK_030091}They really give me the heebie-jeebies.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "So I'd rather not go into that grave if\n"
    .string "we can avoid it at all...\n"
    .string "But, {PLAYER}, this doesn't seem\n"
    .string "to bother you very much...\n"
    .string "Either you're very much in control of\n"
    .string "your fear...\n"
    .string "Or you haven't really registered what's\n"
    .string "going on here...$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Fine, fine!! {COLOR}{RED}King Gustaf{COLOR}{WHITE} is waiting for\n"
    .string "us inside that crypt!\n"
    .string "And remember, it IS the Royal Crypt, so\n"
    .string "show a little respect in there!\n"
    .string "Got that, {PLAYER}?$"
    .string "{UNK_030091}Sooo... Meeting a dead king means...{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}He must have had unfinished business\n"
    .string "in the world of the living.\n"
    .string "He seemed awfully polite for a ghost.\n"
    .string "I expected...spookier, I suppose.\n"
    .string "What do you suppose he meant by all\n"
    .string "that {QT}{COLOR}{RED}source of the flow{COLOR}{WHITE}{QT} business?{UNK_010A}$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}{QT}{COLOR}{RED}The source of the flow{COLOR}{WHITE}{QT}...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "In other words, a place that the water\n"
    .string "comes from, wouldn't you say?\n"
    .string "Now, ask yourself: {COLOR}{YELLOW}where does all the\n"
    .string "water{COLOR}{WHITE} in Hyrule {COLOR}{YELLOW}come from{COLOR}{WHITE}?$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}We only need to find one more {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "And while we don't know exactly where it\n"
    .string "is, we've got a good lead to follow!\n"
    .string "I'm sure we'll be on the right track if\n"
    .string "we find Gustaf's {QT}{COLOR}{RED}source of the flow{COLOR}{WHITE}{QT}!\n"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Let's go, {PLAYER}!!$"
    .string "{UNK_030090}Of course! The {COLOR}{RED}source of the flow{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "He meant {COLOR}{RED}Veil Springs{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "I wonder what lies up ahead...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Well, we know it's connected to the\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE}, so let's go, {PLAYER}!$"
    .string "What's happening to the {COLOR}{RED}source\n"
    .string "of the water{COLOR}{WHITE}?\n"
    .string "There shouldn't be anything but\n"
    .string "blue sky up there!\n"
    .string "Well, no point sitting around thinking\n"
    .string "about it!\n"
    .string "... ...{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}Hey, I just realized something.{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}I'm starting to think...and talk...\n"
    .string "a lot like you lately! What's with that?{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}{UNK_03008D}I need to get my head straight!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}There must be {COLOR}{YELLOW}something{COLOR}{WHITE} just beyond\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}Veil Springs{COLOR}{WHITE} that leads to the {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "We're just one step away from being\n"
    .string "able to lift {COLOR}{RED}Princess Zelda{COLOR}{WHITE}'s curse!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}A world of clouds high above\n"
    .string "the ground...\n"
    .string "I feel like I've seen it all now!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{PLAYER}, perhaps it would be\n"
    .string "best if you didn't look down.\n"
    .string "One false step and...{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}{UNK_030090}I don't even want to think about it!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Nothing but clouds, as far as the eye\n"
    .string "can see!\n"
    .string "But there's got to be a clue to the\n"
    .string "final {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE}'s location somewhere!\n"
    .string "Keep those eyes peeled, {PLAYER}!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}That tornado near {COLOR}{RED}Veil Springs {COLOR}{WHITE}took us\n"
    .string "to this cloud world! Can you believe it?\n"
    .string "I don't know what awaits us next, \n"
    .string "but I can't wait to find out!\n"
    .string "... ...{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}Hm? Hey, {PLAYER}!!\n"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Don't get all scared on me now!\n"
    .string "Show me some spirit, lad!\n"
    .string "Let's enjoy ourselves!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}The people who live on the clouds must\n"
    .string "know something of the last {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "We should certainly ask, at any rate!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}What is it, {PLAYER}?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Weren't we going to ask the wind folk\n"
    .string "here about that last element?$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}We come all this way to the clouds, and\n"
    .string "we have ANOTHER building to explore?\n"
    .string "And what's holding that thing up\n"
    .string "in the first place?\n"
    .string "{UNK_030092}{PLAYER}, walk very carefully up\n"
    .string "here, you got that!?$"
    .string "{UNK_030090}Wow, a {COLOR}{RED}Palace of Winds{COLOR}{WHITE} atop a\n"
    .string "field of clouds... How elegant.\n"
    .string "But that's not our first concern.\n"
    .string "The monsters here are pretty tough.\n"
    .string "Watch your footing, and make sure\n"
    .string "you don't fall!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}So the last {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE} is in the deepest\n"
    .string "recesses of the {COLOR}{RED}Palace of Winds{COLOR}{WHITE}...\n"
    .string "We've finally done it, {PLAYER}!\n"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}You know what you have to do now!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Whoa!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Maybe fighting the flow isn't what we're\n"
    .string "supposed to be doing here...\n"
    .string "Perhaps we should just let it carry\n"
    .string "us along for a bit.\n"
    .string "If you can't beat 'em, join 'em, right?$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}{PLAYER}! I'm overcome!\n"
    .string "We've got all the {COLOR}{GREEN}elements{COLOR}{WHITE} now!\n"
    .string "Now we can revive the {COLOR}{GREEN}sacred blade{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "You'll have {COLOR}{RED}Princess Zelda{COLOR}{WHITE} back to\n"
    .string "normal in no time!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}This will go down in legend!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "To think that I will witness the\n"
    .string "rebirth of the {COLOR}{GREEN}sacred blade{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "I can barely contain myself! Quickly!\n"
    .string "Quickly! To the {COLOR}{RED}elemental sanctuary{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}The king and the guards must not be\n"
    .string "able to see it...\n"
    .string "But the entrance to the {COLOR}{RED}elemental\n"
    .string "sanctuary {COLOR}{WHITE}is right in the courtyard!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}How...could he?! {COLOR}{RED}Vaati {COLOR}{WHITE}will pay for this!{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}{UNK_030092}{PLAYER}! Now is the time to use the\n"
    .string "true power of the sacred {COLOR}{GREEN}Four Sword{COLOR}{WHITE}!!\n"
    .string "You can {COLOR}{YELLOW}lift the curse{COLOR}{WHITE} from each of\n"
    .string "these people, one by one!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}{COLOR}{RED}Hyrule Castle{COLOR}{WHITE} has fallen into darkness.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "This place is a den of evil for {COLOR}{RED}Vaati{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "and his beast minions now...\n"
    .string "I understand your haste, but it may\n"
    .string "be wise to retreat for now...\n"
    .string "Just until we've prepared ourselves to\n"
    .string "face this challenge anew!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}{COLOR}{RED}Hyrule Castle{COLOR}{WHITE} has become a castle of\n"
    .string "darkness now, and I fear for the {COLOR}{RED}king{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "{PLAYER}! You are the only one in all\n"
    .string "of Hyrule who can save those people!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}If Vaati is after the {COLOR}{GREEN}light force{COLOR}{WHITE}, he\n"
    .string "won't stop until he's drained {COLOR}{RED}Zelda{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "I doubt she will be able to survive the\n"
    .string "extraction process...\n"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}{PLAYER}! We must hurry to the roof\n"
    .string "of {COLOR}{RED}Hyrule Castle{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}We will get through this!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "We have all of the techniques and\n"
    .string "power you've gained in your journey!\n"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}And we have your wisdom and courage\n"
    .string "as well! {PLAYER}! I believe in you!$"
    .string "{UNK_030091}Hyrule Castle has grown dark...\n"
    .string "Perhaps this repulsive scene...\n"
    .string "is just a reflection of the evil lurking\n"
    .string "in the heart of my former student.\n"
    .string "... ...{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "{UNK_0101}Ah, what have I created?\n"
    .string "But don't worry about me, {PLAYER}!\n"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}I know what we must do!!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}We have no time!!\n"
    .string "We must get to Princess Zelda!!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}What are you doing talking to me!!\n"
    .string "We have no time for this!!\n"
    .string "Let's go, {PLAYER}!!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}{COLOR}{RED}Princess Zelda{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "{PLAYER} and I are on the way!!\n"
    .string "Wait for us! We're coming!!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Well done, {PLAYER}!\n"
    .string "I knew you could do it!!\n"
    .string "Now! Let's {COLOR}{YELLOW}remove that curse{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "from {COLOR}{RED}Princess Zelda{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Hold on just a little longer, Your\n"
    .string "Highness!\n"
    .string "Come on, {PLAYER}! Hurry up and\n"
    .string "return {COLOR}{RED}Princess Zelda{COLOR}{WHITE} to normal!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}It's been a long road, but we're\n"
    .string "almost there. After all...\n"
    .string "The sacred {COLOR}{GREEN}Four Sword{COLOR}{WHITE} that you carry\n"
    .string "must be able to remove the curse!\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}Princess Zelda{COLOR}{WHITE} will be restored!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}It's dangerous here!\n"
    .string "{PLAYER}!\n"
    .string "Let's get the princess to the\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}elemental sanctuary{COLOR}{WHITE} quickly!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}Now that Vaati's power is fading,\n"
    .string "this place is crumbling!\n"
    .string "{UNK_030092}{PLAYER}!! {COLOR}{RED}Princess Zelda{COLOR}{WHITE}!!\n"
    .string "Watch your footing!!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}As soon as we take care of one\n"
    .string "problem, another one comes up!\n"
    .string "{PLAYER}, I'm sorry to have to\n"
    .string "say this...\n"
    .string "But you'll have to save your joyful\n"
    .string "reunion with {COLOR}{RED}Zelda{COLOR}{WHITE} for another time.$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}It's nice taking in the view from up\n"
    .string "here and all, but...\n"
    .string "I'm thinking maybe I should be a\n"
    .string "little higher up by now...\n"
    .string "What I'm trying to say here, kid, is...\n"
    .string "have you been drinking your milk?$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Hey, kid! Kid!\n"
    .string "Slow down a little!\n"
    .string "You seem to have completely forgotten\n"
    .string "that I'm on top of your head here!\n"
    .string "Man, I hate to think of how this is\n"
    .string "going to play out...{UNK_010A}$"
    .string "{UNK_0106}{UNK_030090}ZZZZZ.......\n"
    .string "{UNK_0102}Huh? Whuzza--! What?!\n"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}What are you talking about?!\n"
    .string "Me? Sleeping? That's crazy!\n"
    .string "{UNK_0106}{UNK_030090}Mmmmnumumummm...$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Yes? What's the matter, m'boy?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "What? You were just checking up on\n"
    .string "me? What's that about!?!\n"
    .string "You think I just sit on your head,\n"
    .string "waiting at your beck and call?\n"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}I can't believe it! Grumble, grumble...$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Hey, kid! Could you lend me a hand?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}I've got a nasty back itch, and I can't\n"
    .string "reach it with my beak.\n"
    .string "Could you please scratch me\n"
    .string "right there?\n"
    .string "No, up! Up! OK, now to the left!\n"
    .string "I said left!\n"
    .string "... ...{UNK_010A}\n"
    .string "{UNK_030090}{UNK_0102}{COLOR}{YELLOW}Ohhh, sweet mercy!{T_0B}{UNK_0103}{UNK_0104}{UNK_0105}{UNK_0104}{UNK_0103}{UNK_0102}{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "That's the stuff!\n"
    .string "{UNK_030092}{UNK_0101}Thanks, buddy! I owe you one!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Hey! Hey! Stop twirling around like that!\n"
    .string "You're giving me the spins, kid!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}Man, I could really go for a nice,\n"
    .string "hot bath right now...\n"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Huh?! What's that?!\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{YELLOW}You'd send me to the cleaners!?{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}What makes you think you can treat\n"
    .string "me like common laundry, huh?$"
    .string "Mmmmnum"
    .string "umummm...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Come on, please...\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{YELLOW}Just five more minutes...{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "{UNK_030090}I promise I'll get up in five minutes...$"
    .string "{UNK_030090}Mnyawwwn... I don't know why\n"
    .string "I'm so tired...\n"
    .string "I guess I just get a little bored sitting\n"
    .string "up here, watching you wander around.$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Do you have to ask me about every\n"
    .string "single little thing?!\n"
    .string "Just figure it out for yourself,\n"
    .string "you big baby!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Oh, NOW you need me?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "I was starting to think you'd forgotten\n"
