    .string "Wow... I just had the best idea! I can\n"
    .string "rent out my house for some extra cash!$"
    .string "I'm feeling really motivated now!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "I could probably build a good-sized\n"
    .string "house in a matter of minutes!$"
    .string "My special {COLOR}{GREEN}red potion {COLOR}{WHITE}is almost finished!\n"
    .string "Oh, and it's so very special!\n"
    .string "Heeheehee!$"
    .string "Hey! I've just hit on a great idea!\n"
    .string "This will add a little more risk!\n"
    .string "Heh heh heh! I'm so excited!\n"
    .string "I can't wait to get started!$"
    .string "I really wish I could do more to help\n"
    .string "people...\n"
    .string "Wait! I've got it! I'll ask {COLOR}{RED}Swiftblade {COLOR}{WHITE}to\n"
    .string "start up a newsletter for adventurers!\n"
    .string "That'll be a great way to provide\n"
    .string "a useful service for everyone...\n"
    .string "Hm. It's going to be a lot of work,\n"
    .string "though. I should get {COLOR}{RED}Marcy {COLOR}{WHITE}to help me.$"
    .string "You know what would be great? A bomb\n"
    .string "that went off only when you wanted...\n"
    .string "Hm... Actually, I think I could probably\n"
    .string "make one with just a few minor tweaks!$"
    .string "It's been a long time since the last time\n"
    .string "I visited {COLOR}{RED}Hyrule{COLOR}{WHITE}...\n"
    .string "I think I'll set up a little place\n"
    .string "where I can sell my Kinstones.$"
    .string "{UNK_0301BE}I don't know why I've been such a\n"
    .string "nasty little prankster all the time...\n"
    .string "All of a sudden, I feel like a weight's\n"
    .string "been lifted off my shoulders!\n"
    .string "I feel like I've made up for all my\n"
    .string "awful deeds! Haha!\n"
    .string "Hey, {COLOR}{RED}Spookter{COLOR}{WHITE}! See you in paradise!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301B7}I feel so much stronger now!\n"
    .string "Here we go!!!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301BA}Whew! It's about time... Looking good,\n"
    .string "though! I'm going in!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301B9}Hn... No, it's no good...\n"
    .string "I can't break it by myself.$"
    .string "{UNK_0301B8}I had a strange feeling, like a fellow\n"
    .string "Goron was in need... Hello? Goro?\n"
    .string "Hn? That wall! You can't get through\n"
    .string "that alone! I'm coming to help you!!!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301B7}Don't worry! I'm here to help you! Let's\n"
    .string "break through that wall together! Goro!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301B7}Hn... This wall is pretty tough. I don't\n"
    .string "think just the two of us can break it.\n"
    .string "But that doesn't mean we're going\n"
    .string "to stop trying! Goro!!!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301B8}I thought I smelled some Gorons around\n"
    .string "here! What are you guys up to?$"
    .string "{UNK_0301BA}Hey! Give us a hand breaking\n"
    .string "through this wall! Goro!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301B9}That's a tough wall! The three of us\n"
    .string "together couldn't even break it...$"
    .string "{UNK_0301B8}I smell delicious stones... They're right\n"
    .string "on the other side of this wall.$"
    .string "{UNK_0301B7}Can you give me a hand? Gorogoro?$"
    .string "{UNK_0301B7}That's one solid wall... No doubt about\n"
    .string "it. We're going to need some more help.$"
    .string "{UNK_0301B9}Oooo... I can smell deliciousness just\n"
    .string "on the other side of that wall.$"
    .string "{UNK_0301B7}Oh, thank goodness! Help has arrived!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301BA}Almost there... Goro! But it's\n"
    .string "still just not breaking!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301B7}I had a feeling there were some Gorons\n"
    .string "in need of a little extra muscle.\n"
    .string "Well, I'm here to help!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301BA}Hey, perfect timing! All right, everyone!\n"
    .string "Together now! Gooooroooo!!!$"
