, 0x23, 0x15, 0x00, 0x00, 0x4b, 0x16, 0x00, 0x00, 0xc8, 0x16, 0x00, 0x00, 0xfe, 0x17, 0x00, 0x00, 0x3a, 0x18, 0x00, 0x00, 0xd2, 0x18, 0x00, 0x00, 0x06, 0x19, 0x00, 0x00, 0x4c, 0x1a, 0x00, 0x00, 0x90, 0x1a, 0x00, 0x00, 0x62, 0x1b, 0x00, 0x00, 0x83, 0x1b, 0x00, 0x00, 0xe4, 0x1b, 0x00, 0x00, 0x4d, 0x1c, 0x00, 0x00, 0xa6, 0x1c, 0x00, 0x00, 0xa7, 0x1c, 0x00, 0x00, 0x68, 0x1d, 0x00, 0x00, 0x91, 0x1d, 0x00, 0x00, 0xd6, 0x1d, 0x00, 0x00, 0x0e, 0x1e, 0x00, 0x00, 0x21, 0x1e, 0x00, 0x00, 0x01, 0x1f, 0x00, 0x00, 0xa2, 0x1f, 0x00, 0x00, 0xa3, 0x1f, 0x00, 0x00, 0xc8, 0x20, 0x00, 0x00, 0x18, 0x21, 0x00, 0x00, 0xaf, 0x21, 0x00, 0x00, 0xe3, 0x21, 0x00, 0x00, 0x19, 0x23, 0x00, 0x00, 0x1a, 0x23, 0x00, 0x00, 0x3e, 0x23, 0x00, 0x00, 0x3f, 0x23, 0x00, 0x00, 0x40, 0x23, 0x00, 0x00, 0x41, 0x23, 0x00, 0x00, 0x42, 0x23, 0x00, 0x00, 0xa1, 0x23, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x03, 0x00, 0x95
    .string "Good morning, {COLOR}{RED}Master Smith{COLOR}{WHITE}.$"
    .string "{UNK_0300C2}Goodness me! {COLOR}{RED}Princess Zelda{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Did you sneak out of the castle\n"
    .string "and come all this way alone?\n"
    .string "The minister is sure to be worried\n"
    .string "about you! You know how he gets!$"
    .string "Oh, don't worry about him! He'll be fine.\n"
    .string "Where's {PLAYER}?\n"
    .string "The whole town is bustling for the\n"
    .string "annual {COLOR}{YELLOW}Picori Festival{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "I thought he and I might go together.\n"
    .string "Would you mind terribly?$"
    .string "Oh, is that what you're here for? \n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Well, {PLAYER} was up late helping me\n"
    .string "last night, and he's still asleep...\n"
    .string "But I do have an errand at the\n"
    .string "castle... Yes, that should be fine.\n"
    .string "{UNK_071005}$"
    .string "{PLAYER}, time to get up!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_041000}Hey! {PLAYER}!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}Princess Zelda{COLOR}{WHITE} is here. She'd like to\n"
    .string "know if you'd join her at the festival.$"
    .string "Yeah, {PLAYER}. Come on! Let's\n"
    .string "go check out the festival together!\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}Master Smith{COLOR}{WHITE} already gave me\n"
    .string "permission to take you!$"
    .string "{UNK_041000}Yes. After all, the festival only comes\n"
    .string "once a year. Go on, have fun!\n"
    .string "And while you're there, you can do me\n"
    .string "a favor.\n"
    .string "I just finished making this {COLOR}{GREEN}sword {COLOR}{WHITE}for\n"
    .string "the minister at {COLOR}{RED}Hyrule Castle{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "I'd like you to deliver it to him.$"
    .string "{UNK_041000}This is the blade that will be presented\n"
    .string "to the winner of the competition.\n"
    .string "Don't lose it. And while the two of you\n"
    .string "may be childhood friends, remember...\n"
    .string "{UNK_07100E}$"
    .string "Master Smith, quit worrying! We'll be\n"
    .string "perfectly safe.\n"
    .string "Come on, {PLAYER}! Let's go\n"
    .string "check out the festival!$"
    .string "{UNK_041000}Zelda is the princess of Hyrule.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "You watch over her. Don't let\n"
    .string "anything bad happen to her.$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_030094}{PLAYER}! Over here!\n"
    .string "$"
    .string "Come on, {PLAYER}. Let's hurry\n"
    .string "to the castle.$"
    .string "{UNK_030095}{PLAYER}!\n"
    .string "Hurry! Let's go!$"
    .string "Over here! Come on!\n"
    .string "Hurry up!$"
    .string "Well, here we are! The {COLOR}{RED}town of Hyrule{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "We have a winner!$"
    .string "Oh, my! Princess Zelda! You won the\n"
    .string "grand prize in our drawing? Wow!\n"
    .string "You get your choice of any of these\n"
    .string "wonderful prizes. What will it be?$"
    .string "First, we have...this lovely\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{GREEN}heart-shaped stone{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "Next, we have...$"
    .string "this {COLOR}{GREEN}magnificent gem{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "And finally, there's...$"
    .string "this teeny-tiny {COLOR}{GREEN}shield{COLOR}{WHITE}.$"
    .string "So, which one would you like?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Let me guess...the jewel? Oh, but this\n"
    .string "heart stone is very cute, too.\n"
    .string "Choose whichever one you like!\n"
    .string "$"
    .string "The {COLOR}{GREEN}shield {COLOR}{WHITE}is so adorable! I think\n"
    .string "I'll take it.$"
    .string "What!? Why? Why would you want that\n"
    .string "ugly thing!?\n"
    .string "What about the heart stone! It's cute!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Or... Or this giant gem! It's pretty!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Honestly, they're both much nicer than\n"
    .string "that nasty little shield thing.$"
    .string "Nope! I want the {COLOR}{GREEN}shield{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "Can I have it?$"
    .string "What a strange princess you are.\n"
    .string "Well...\n"
    .string "OK. Here's your teeny-tiny {COLOR}{GREEN}shield{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "$"
    .string "Here! I want to give you a present!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Doesn't this {COLOR}{GREEN}shield{COLOR}{WHITE} suit you perfectly,\n"
    .string "{PLAYER}?$"
    .string "Yep! Just as I thought! You look great!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Now, if anything happens, you can\n"
    .string "protect me with that shield!\n"
    .string "Oh! I almost forgot! We have to {COLOR}{YELLOW}take\n"
    .string "Master Smith's sword to the castle{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "Let's go, {PLAYER}.$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_04100C}{UNK_0300A9}Oh! {PLAYER}! You brought the\n"
    .string "sword, did you?\n"
    .string "Then, as minister to the kingdom of\n"
    .string "Hyrule, I, {COLOR}{RED}Potho{COLOR}{WHITE}, accept this blade.\n"
    .string "You came just in time. The award\n"
    .string "ceremony will begin soon.$"
    .string "{UNK_030094}{UNK_04100C}I'm sorry, {PLAYER}, but I'd better go.\n"
    .string "I have to prepare for the ceremony.\n"
    .string "I had a good time at the festival.\n"
    .string "Thanks for coming with me!$"
    .string "Since you're here, {PLAYER}, why don't\n"
    .string "you join us for the award ceremony?$"
    .string "Do you know about {COLOR}{GREEN}that sword{COLOR}{WHITE},\n"
    .string "{PLAYER}?\n"
    .string "It is called the {COLOR}{GREEN}Picori Blade{COLOR}{WHITE}, and it\n"
    .string "locks much evil away in that chest.\n"
    .string "The {COLOR}{GREEN}Picori Blade{COLOR}{WHITE} is sacred among the\n"
    .string "people of Hyrule.\n"
    .string "The legend has it that, long ago, the\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}Picori{COLOR}{WHITE} gave us this blade.\n"
    .string "Whoever wins the competition earns the\n"
    .string "honor of touching the sacred blade.$"
    .string "{UNK_0301F2}Let the award ceremony commence!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}Vaati{COLOR}{WHITE}, champion of the competition,\n"
    .string "you may approach the blade!$"
    .string "{UNK_0300AA}Ah! Princess Zelda!! Wh--\n"
    .string "When did you leave the castle?!$"
    .string "{UNK_0300AA}Welcome to {COLOR}{RED}Hyrule Castle{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "Sorry, but we're getting things ready\n"
    .string "for the ceremony. I can't let you pass.$"
    .string "Preparations for the award ceremony\n"
    .string "are coming along nicely.$"
    .string "Sorry, but I can't let you pass. We've\n"
    .string "sealed the area off because of {COLOR}{RED}Vaati{COLOR}{WHITE}.$"
    .string "Ah, the sword for the award ceremony!\n"
    .string "You should take that to {COLOR}{RED}Minister Potho{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "You'll find him in front of the castle.$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "Heh heh heh...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "To think things would go this well!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "The {COLOR}{GREEN}Picori Blade{COLOR}{WHITE} and the Bound Chest\n"
    .string "spoken of in Hylian lore...\n"
    .string "This chest must hold that which I seek!\n"
    .string "I'll relieve you of its contents now.$"
    .string "{UNK_03009B}Mmmm ah hah hah hah!\n"
    .string "Do not interfere with me...\n"
    .string "As victor, I've earned the right to\n"
    .string "approach the {COLOR}{GREEN}Picori Blade{COLOR}{WHITE}...\n"
    .string "I've been waiting for this moment!$"
    .string "Who are you? Why are you doing this?$"
    .string "The princess with the {COLOR}{YELLOW}mystic aura{COLOR}{WHITE}...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "...The power that was gifted to the\n"
    .string "people of Hyrule still flows\n"
    .string "within the veins of the ladies\n"
    .string "of its royal family? Interesting...\n"
    .string "If I leave you now, you'll only cause\n"
    .string "me trouble later. That will never do.$"
    .string "To stone with you!$"
    .string "{PLAYER}! Watch out!\n"
    .string "\t$"
    .string "$"
    .string "...?!?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Empty? There was nothing in there\n"
    .string "but a rabble of monsters?\n"
    .string "What is the meaning of this?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Well, I know the {COLOR}{GREEN}force{COLOR}{WHITE} I'm after is\n"
    .string "somewhere out there.\n"
    .string "I'm in no hurry. I can take my\n"
    .string "time searching for it.\n"
    .string "{UNK_03009B}Heh heh heh...$"
    .string "Heh heh heh heh... All who stand\n"
    .string "in my way shall share this fate!\n"
    .string "Now, to find out what power awaits\n"
    .string "me in this chest!$"
    .string "Eeeeeeeek!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_0300A3}It is as you have all heard.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "A sorcerer named {COLOR}{RED}Vaati{COLOR}{WHITE} has cursed my\n"
    .string "fair Zelda and turned her to stone.\n"
    .string "If we had the sacred {COLOR}{GREEN}Picori Blade{COLOR}{WHITE}, we\n"
    .string "likely could have broken the curse.\n"
    .string "But Vaati shattered the blade...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "However, I have not given up hope.\n"
    .string "What do you know about the {COLOR}{RED}Picori{COLOR}{WHITE}?$"
    .string "The {COLOR}{RED}Picori{COLOR}{WHITE}? Not much, beyond what the\n"
    .string "fairy tales say...\n"
    .string "They're supposed to be very tiny, if I'm\n"
    .string "remembering correctly.$"
    .string "Yes, the ones from the fairy tales...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "But the Picori are no mere legend.\n"
    .string "They most certainly exist.\n"
    .string "No one outside of the royal family\n"
    .string "knows the truth about them.\n"
    .string "The Picori, who forged the sacred\n"
    .string "blade, live deep within {COLOR}{RED}Minish Woods{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "They should be able to repair the\n"
    .string "broken blade and reforge the sword.$"
    .string "Wh-What!? Then we must dispatch the\n"
    .string "soldiers there at once!$"
    .string "No, soldiers will not do.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "The Picori do not show themselves\n"
    .string "to anyone but children.\n"
    .string "Our soldiers could search for days\n"
    .string "and still find no sign of them.$"
    .string "I see...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "If that's the case, then why not\n"
    .string "send {PLAYER}?$"
    .string "{UNK_0301EB}If {PLAYER} has recovered, then yes,\n"
    .string "I would like to ask this of him.\n"
    .string "Please, turn my precious Zelda back\n"
    .string "to normal.\n"
    .string "The {COLOR}{RED}Picori{COLOR}{WHITE} should know how to create a\n"
    .string "new {COLOR}{GREEN}sacred sword{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "It will be a dangerous journey, now\n"
    .string "that those monsters have been freed.\n"
    .string "Please, take this sword with you,\n"
    .string "along with the broken {COLOR}{GREEN}Picori Blade{COLOR}{WHITE}.$"
    .string "Very well, then. Send the soldiers to\n"
    .string "search for {COLOR}{RED}Vaati{COLOR}{WHITE} at once!$"
    .string "Deep within the {COLOR}{RED}Minish Woods{COLOR}{WHITE}, you will\n"
    .string "find a place called {COLOR}{RED}Deepwood Shrine{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "Once, humans and {COLOR}{RED}Picori{COLOR}{WHITE} shared that\n"
    .string "shrine as a meeting place.\n"
    .string "I think it would be best if you\n"
    .string "started your search there.$"
    .string "Take this {COLOR}{GREEN}map {COLOR}{WHITE}with you.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{UNK_07105E}$"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}Minish Woods{COLOR}{WHITE} lies southeast\n"
    .string "of the town of Hyrule.\n"
    .string "In fact, it's due east of your\n"
    .string "house, {PLAYER}.$"
    .string "Oh, {PLAYER}. You're awake. Are you\n"
    .string "feeling all right?\n"
    .string "Stand at my side. The king of\n"
    .string "Hyrule is about to speak.$"
    .string "I am counting on you, {PLAYER}.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Only you can break {COLOR}{YELLOW}Vaati's curse\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{WHITE}and free Princess Zelda.$"
    .string "$"
    .string "If you get lost on your way to the\n"
    .string "forest, simply check your map.\n"
    .string "Just press START and then {LEFT} or\n"
    .string "{RIGHT} to open the map.\n"
    .string "I've marked the location of the forest\n"
    .string "for you. Good luck, and be careful.$"
    .string "Oh, thank goodness!\n"
    .string "You've awakened!\n"
    .string "{UNK_071060}$"
    .string "Master Smith is here as well. He's come\n"
    .string "to see His Majesty the king.$"
    .string "Please find a way to break the curse\n"
    .string "on Princess Zelda.$"
    .string "Please be careful!$"
    .string "Press {RIGHT} while walking to roll. This\n"
    .string "is useful when you want to move fast.\n"
    .string "Don't forget! And if you want to {COLOR}{YELLOW}save{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "during the game, press {COLOR}{YELLOW}START{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "and choose SAVE from the {COLOR}{YELLOW}Items\n"
    .string "screen{COLOR}{WHITE} or the {COLOR}{YELLOW}Quest Status screen{COLOR}{WHITE}.$"
    .string "There are monsters outside the castle.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "If you see one, use your {COLOR}{GREEN}shield{COLOR}{WHITE} to\n"
    .string "defend yourself.\n"
    .string "Move in close enough to use your {COLOR}{GREEN}sword{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "if you need to fight.$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E0}Owwwwch!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "That must be the {COLOR}{RED}Business Scrub{COLOR}{WHITE} I\n"
    .string "heard the soldiers talking about.\n"
    .string "They were saying a Deku Scrub had\n"
    .string "been hassling all the passersby.\n"
    .string "{PLAYER}, do something about it!\n"
    .string "Otherwise, we can't get to the castle.\n"
    .string "If only we had some way to defend\n"
    .string "ourselves against {COLOR}{YELLOW}those nuts of his{COLOR}{WHITE}.$"
    .string "If we could just defend against those\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{YELLOW}nuts{COLOR}{WHITE}, I'm sure we could do something!$"
    .string "I actually feel a little sorry for that\n"
    .string "Business Scrub. But that nut hurt!\n"
    .string "Oh, well. He won't be hassling anyone\n"
    .string "now! We'd better hurry to the castle!$"
    .string "Where are you going, {PLAYER}?\n"
    .string "Hurry up and do something!$"
    .string "Please! Forgive me, sir!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "I heard there was a {COLOR}{YELLOW}festival{COLOR}{WHITE}, and I\n"
    .string "came to {COLOR}{RED}town {COLOR}{WHITE}hoping to hawk my wares.\n"
    .string "Unfortunately, we scrubs have a\n"
    .string "tendency to spit nuts when we speak!\n"
    .string "Everyone got scared and ran away,\n"
    .string "and no one would buy anything!\n"
    .string "This is a terrible place to do\n"
    .string "business! I'm going back to my cave!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "All right! To the {COLOR}{RED}castle {COLOR}{WHITE}we go!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "Even turned to stone by {COLOR}{YELLOW}Vaati's\n"
    .string "curse{COLOR}{WHITE}, her eyes are filled with life.\n"
    .string "Hurry... Save her...$"
