    .string "Helllllp!!! Help meeee!!!$"
    .string "Ouch! Won't somebody stop them!?$"
    .string "Ow! Ow! Help... Somebody!\n"
    .string "Can't anybody hear me?$"
    .string "OUCH!!!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Hey! Kid! You there!$"
    .string "Ow!$"
    .string "Hey! Don't just stand there!\n"
    .string "Do something!!!$"
    .string "Ow!$"
    .string "What's wrong with you!? Do you like\n"
    .string "watching me take this abuse!? Help me!$"
    .string "{UNK_030090}Phew! Well done! That was close. Not\n"
    .string "that I couldn't handle them myself.\n"
    .string "But that's beside the point!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "What in the world is a lone child\n"
    .string "doing so deep in the woods?$"
    .string "Ho ho! I see.$"
    .string "The...{COLOR}{RED}Picori{COLOR}{WHITE}, you say? And {COLOR}{RED}Vaati{COLOR}{WHITE}?$"
    .string "Vaati's cursed someone? What?\n"
    .string "The sacred blade?!?$"
    .string "Is that so? I see, I see... You know,\n"
    .string "you and I have quite a lot in common.\n"
    .string "You see, I, too, am on a quest to\n"
    .string "break a curse of Vaati's.\n"
    .string "And you say that reforging the {COLOR}{GREEN}sacred\n"
    .string "blade{COLOR}{WHITE} can break his curse, eh?\n"
    .string "Well, then you have found yourself\n"
    .string "a companion, my boy!\n"
    .string "My name is {COLOR}{RED}Ezlo{COLOR}{WHITE}. It's a pleasure to\n"
    .string "make your acquaintance.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Wait! Wait, I say!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "You walk so quickly!\n"
    .string "Too quickly, in fact!\n"
    .string "Can't you go any slower? Surely\n"
    .string "you've noticed that I have no legs...$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Boy! Take a good look at me! Do you\n"
    .string "really think I can walk that fast!?$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E4}Augh!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "If it isn't one thing, it's another!\n"
    .string "You are a troublesome boy!$"
    .string "{UNK_03005F}There! Now, you can't possibly\n"
    .string "leave me behind.\n"
    .string "My... It's quite comfortable up here.\n"
    .string "More comfortable than it looks, surely.\n"
    .string "And much easier on me!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Hey! Quit your squirming! Can't\n"
    .string "you sit still? See! There...\n"
    .string "Yes, yes! That's it. Much better.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Now, I suppose a boy like you still has\n"
    .string "much to learn about the world.\n"
    .string "If ever you need my insight, press\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{YELLOW}SELECT{COLOR}{WHITE}. I'll be happy to help!\n"
    .string "Ah, such a hopeless child...$"
    .string "Hey! Where are you going?\n"
    .string "You heartless brat! Help me!!!$"
    .string "What are you doing? Aren't you going\n"
    .string "to finish them off?$"
    .string "...What? Is there something on my\n"
    .string "face? Quit staring! It's rude!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "Oh, {PLAYER}. You're heading for\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}Minish Woods{COLOR}{WHITE} now, aren't you?\n"
    .string "Leave the monsters that {COLOR}{RED}Vaati\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{WHITE}freed to us, and go find the {COLOR}{RED}Picori{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
