    .string "here. If you get lost, check your {COLOR}{GREEN}map{COLOR}{WHITE}.$"
    .string "$"
    .string "Hey, kid! Where are you going!?\n"
    .string "That's the way we just came from!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "You who desire to enter the realm of\n"
    .string "the Minish, seek out the hidden portal.\n"
    .string "Offer up your song at the portal's\n"
    .string "base, and be guided to the world below.$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}Hmmm... It appears we have found the\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}Minish village{COLOR}{WHITE}.$"
    .string "{UNK_0300B1}Pico picori!$"
    .string "{UNK_0300B3}Ripi ripico picori!$"
    .string "{UNK_0300B2}Picoco pico ripico!$"
    .string "I gather it's been quite some time\n"
    .string "since they last saw a human.\n"
    .string "...What's that? You didn't understand\n"
    .string "what they were saying just now?\n"
    .string "Ah, yes. That was the language\n"
    .string "of the {COLOR}{RED}Minish{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "It's a little different from the dialect\n"
    .string "I am most familiar with.\n"
    .string "I'm afraid I didn't catch most\n"
    .string "of what they said myself.\n"
    .string "But perhaps there is someone here\n"
    .string "who {COLOR}{YELLOW}understands your language{COLOR}{WHITE}."
    .string "\n"
    .string "We should look around.$"
    .string "$"
    .string "Fortunately, the {COLOR}{GREEN}Earth Element {COLOR}{WHITE}is in the\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}shrine {COLOR}{WHITE}at the far end of the village.\n"
    .string "A horde of beasts lives in that {COLOR}{RED}shrine{COLOR}{WHITE},\n"
    .string "though, so enter with caution.$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_03020D}Oh! You speak our language!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "It's been quite a while since we've\n"
    .string "heard outsiders speak our tongue!\n"
    .string "We have little to offer you in these\n"
    .string "woods, but please, enjoy your stay.$"
    .string "Thank you for your offer, but we have\n"
    .string "no time to relax. My name is {COLOR}{RED}Ezlo{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "This child is {PLAYER}.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "We need to break a {COLOR}{YELLOW}curse {COLOR}{WHITE}that has\n"
    .string "been cast on the princess of Hyrule.\n"
    .string "To do so, we'll need to reforge\n"
    .string "the broken {COLOR}{GREEN}Picori Blade{COLOR}{WHITE}.$"
    .string "Ah, yes. And you've come here now\n"
    .string "hoping to have the blade reforged?\n"
    .string "Hm... Well, if that's what you're after,\n"
    .string "you'll need four mystic {COLOR}{GREEN}elements{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "These elements are the crystalline\n"
    .string "forms of the energies of this world.\n"
    .string "Only by {COLOR}{YELLOW}infusing the blade{COLOR}{WHITE} with these\n"
    .string "energies can a new blade be forged.\n"
    .string "Here, give me your map. I can mark\n"
    .string "where these {COLOR}{GREEN}elements{COLOR}{WHITE} can be found.$"
    .string "The {COLOR}{GREEN}Earth Element{COLOR}{WHITE} can be found in the\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}shrine{COLOR}{WHITE} to the north of {COLOR}{RED}Festari{COLOR}{WHITE}'s abbey.\n"
    .string "Speak with {COLOR}{RED}Festari{COLOR}{WHITE}. He will show you the\n"
    .string "path to the {COLOR}{RED}shrine{COLOR}{WHITE}'s entrance.\n"
    .string "Go with caution. Evil creatures have\n"
    .string "lately made their home in our {COLOR}{RED}shrine{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "Return to me at once after you have\n"
    .string "found the {COLOR}{GREEN}Earth Element{COLOR}{WHITE}.$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_03020D}So! You have found the {COLOR}{GREEN}Earth Element{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "You are blessed with much courage and\n"
    .string "strength for one so young.\n"
    .string "If your conviction holds strong, head\n"
    .string "to {COLOR}{RED}Mount Crenel{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "There, you will find a man named {COLOR}{RED}Melari{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Among all the Minish, there is no one\n"
    .string "more able to repair your sword.\n"
    .string "If you ask him, I am certain he will\n"
    .string "reforge your {COLOR}{GREEN}broken Picori Blade{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "I shall send word to him in advance.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Travel safely. You are brave, but\n"
    .string "there are many evils now in the world.$"
    .string "Leave through this door here. It will\n"
    .string "take you out of the forest quickly.$"
    .string "Great elder, we are in your debt.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "We shall head for {COLOR}{RED}Mount Crenel{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "at once!$"
