    .string "{UNK_03009B}Interesting. You're the last person\n"
    .string "I expected to find here.\n"
    .string "And just as I was wondering who could\n"
    .string "be behind this, I find my old master...$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E7}{COLOR}{RED}Vaati{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E9}And, as always, you are dressed in...\n"
    .string "heh heh heh...the shabbiest of rags.\n"
    .string "My {COLOR}{YELLOW}curses{COLOR}{WHITE} are not to be mocked. The\n"
    .string "one I cast on you is most powerful.\n"
    .string "No matter what power you wield, you\n"
    .string "will never break it.$"
    .string "You haven't changed in the slightest.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "I should never have created that {COLOR}{GREEN}cap{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "It only fueled your insane desires!$"
    .string "Fool! A hat that grants the wishes of\n"
    .string "its wearer is a spectacular creation!\n"
    .string "Thanks to you, I have gone from being\n"
    .string "a meek, miniscule nothing to...\n"
    .string "the greatest sorcerer alive!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "You cannot stop me now, and\n"
    .string "I have you to thank for it!\n"
    .string "Accept this small gesture\n"
    .string "of gratitude from me.$"
    .string "Wait! {COLOR}{RED}Vaati{COLOR}{WHITE}, wait!!!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "That foul {COLOR}{RED}Vaati{COLOR}{WHITE}! What could he be\n"
    .string "scheming now?\n"
    .string "{PLAYER}... I feel I owe you an\n"
    .string "explanation of what has happened.\n"
    .string "You see, Vaati and I are both {COLOR}{RED}Minish{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "I was once a famous sage and a\n"
    .string "renowned {COLOR}{RED}Minish {COLOR}{WHITE}craftsman.\n"
    .string "Vaati was only a boy when I took him\n"
    .string "on as my apprentice.\n"
    .string "But...he became enchanted by the\n"
    .string "wickedness in the hearts of men.\n"
    .string "One day, Vaati took a hat I made for\n"
    .string "the humans--my pride and joy.\n"
    .string "It granted the wishes of its wearer.\n"
    .string "He put it on without permission...$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E7}{UNK_041007}Oh! What a vile form you've taken!$"
    .string "{UNK_03009B}Vile? I am a sorcerer now, and my\n"
    .string "power is beyond compare!\n"
    .string "No longer will I tire away as your\n"
    .string "apprentice!\n"
    .string "Now, all shall call ME master!$"
    .string "{UNK_041006}Why, Vaati? What are you plotting?$"
    .string "This year, on the day that comes but\n"
    .string "once a century, the portal opens.\n"
    .string "And when it does, I shall claim the\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{GREEN}light force {COLOR}{WHITE}as my own.\n"
    .string "I will be transformed, perfect, and\n"
    .string "there will be none who can stop me...$"
    .string "GAAAAAA!!!$"
    .string "{UNK_041007}Ah ha ha ha ha ha ha ha!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Tell me, how does it feel,\n"
    .string "my {COLOR}{YELLOW}sorcerer's curse{COLOR}{WHITE}?\n"
    .string "Do you see, Ezlo? I am truly your\n"
    .string "master now, and you cannot stop me.\n"
    .string "And with that, I must be leaving.$"
    .string "Wait! Wait, I tell you!\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}Vaati{COLOR}{WHITE}!!!$"
    .string "You know the legends, of course. The\n"
    .string "gifts the Picori gave the humans...\n"
    .string "What you call the {COLOR}{GREEN}Picori Blade{COLOR}{WHITE} was\n"
    .string "the first of those gifts. The second...\n"
    .string "Well, you call it {COLOR}{GREEN}light force{COLOR}{WHITE}, but it is\n"
    .string "a source of limitless magical power.\n"
    .string "If {COLOR}{RED}Vaati {COLOR}{WHITE}were to get it now, it would\n"
    .string "be devastating.\n"
    .string "I came to the world of men hoping to\n"
    .string "stop Vaati, and I met you in the woods.\n"
    .string "But it seems we won't be breaking\n"
    .string "the curse on me anytime soon.\n"
    .string "However, with the sacred blade, we can\n"
    .string "certainly restore {COLOR}{RED}Princess Zelda{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "I'm sorry. All that has happened has\n"
    .string "been due to my own pride. My folly.\n"
    .string "I must rely on you, on your power,\n"
    .string "until we've put an end to Vaati.$"
    .string "Well, {PLAYER}, enough fairy tales!\n"
    .string "We must search for the next {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "Vaati! What are you doing?$"
    .string "$"
    .string "Eh? What a strange feeling. I sensed\n"
    .string "something from the castle's direction.\n"
    .string "Or...was it just me?$"
    .string "{UNK_0300A3}Hm? Who's there?!?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "What? Vaati! How did you get in here!?$"
    .string "Uhn... What are you doing?!?$"
    .string "{UNK_03009B}Ah ha ha ha ha ha ha ha ha!{UNK_0300A7}$"
    .string "{UNK_0300A9}It looks like you're all here. Very well.\n"
    .string "The king of Hyrule has words for you.$"
    .string "{UNK_0300A3}You all know of the power the Picori\n"
    .string "gave to mankind, do you not?\n"
    .string "The golden {COLOR}{GREEN}light force{COLOR}{WHITE} of limitless\n"
    .string "magical power...\n"
    .string "I want it!!! It is somewhere here in\n"
    .string "Hyrule! Go now, and bring me this power!$"
    .string "Waste no time! Go forth at once, and\n"
    .string "bring me the {COLOR}{GREEN}light force{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "Fling anyone who refuses into the\n"
    .string "dungeon! Him and his family, too!\n"
    .string "I will tolerate no disobedience!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Now, search high and low throughout\n"
    .string "the lands of Hyrule!$"
    .string "Hmm... Maybe it's just the wind...\n"
    .string "But I hope nothing bad has happened.\n"
    .string "Anyway, we need to look for the next\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "The map says it should be\n"
    .string "around here somewhere...$"
    .string "{UNK_0300AA}By the order of the king,\n"
    .string "none shall pass!!\n"
    .string "Now! Begone with you!!$"
    .string "{UNK_0300AA}Hey, you!!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "None may enter!$"
    .string "{UNK_0300AA}I have heard that this castle has\n"
    .string "a {COLOR}{YELLOW}secret entrance{COLOR}{WHITE}...\n"
    .string "If you ever have need of it, you should\n"
    .string "look for that {COLOR}{YELLOW}entrance {COLOR}{WHITE}sometime...$"
    .string "$"
    .string "We are the {COLOR}{RED}Tribe of the Winds{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Long have we lived with the winds. We\n"
    .string "have mastered them. Now, we join them.\n"
    .string "Together, with the great winds at our\n"
    .string "backs, we head for the skies.\n"
    .string "Those who come seeking our power must\n"
    .string "play the {COLOR}{YELLOW}notes{COLOR}{WHITE} Zeffa teaches.\n"
    .string "May they lead you onward to\n"
    .string "the power that you seek.$"
    .string "{UNK_030091}I do believe this is where the\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}Tribe of the Winds{COLOR}{WHITE} once lived.\n"
    .string "Hm... So they've left for the heavens,\n"
    .string "and taken their {COLOR}{GREEN}element{COLOR}{WHITE} with them.\n"
    .string "It looks like the {COLOR}{GREEN}Wind Element {COLOR}{WHITE}is beyond\n"
    .string "our reach for the time being.\n"
    .string "We have no choice but to press on.\n"
    .string "Let's get out of here.$"
    .string "{UNK_0300A3}Oh! {PLAYER}! You have returned!\n"
    .string "And have you found the Picori?\n"
    .string "I see. And they want you to gather\n"
    .string "the {COLOR}{GREEN}four elements{COLOR}{WHITE}?\n"
    .string "Well, it seems I must rely on you once\n"
    .string "more if we are to restore Zelda.\n"
    .string "Please, you must forge the\n"
    .string "sacred blade anew, and quickly!\n"
    .string "I am counting on you, {PLAYER}!$"
    .string "{UNK_0300A9}Oh! {PLAYER}! Tell me, have you\n"
    .string "been taking care of yourself?$"
    .string "{UNK_0300AA}What's that, {PLAYER}? His Majesty\n"
    .string "is in the room in back.$"
    .string "{UNK_0300A3}Oh! {PLAYER}? You have returned!\n"
    .string "Welcome. Did you gather the elements?\n"
    .string "What? A {COLOR}{RED}sanctuary{COLOR}{WHITE}, you say? Why, I've\n"
    .string "heard of no such thing in my castle!$"
    .string "{UNK_0300A9}Hmmm... A {COLOR}{RED}sanctuary{COLOR}{WHITE}...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "You know, I do recall a story my\n"
    .string "grandmother once told me long ago.\n"
    .string "She said she saw a {COLOR}{YELLOW}doorway{COLOR}{WHITE} appear in\n"
    .string "the {COLOR}{YELLOW}palace courtyard{COLOR}{WHITE} as a child.\n"
    .string "If this door does indeed open only once\n"
    .string "a century, it may be open even now!\n"
    .string "As with the Picori themselves, the door\n"
    .string "is visible only to the eyes of a child.\n"
    .string "We might have walked past it recently\n"
    .string "and never even known it was there...$"
    .string "{UNK_0300AA}A {COLOR}{RED}sanctuary{COLOR}{WHITE}? No, I think I'd have seen\n"
    .string "something like that in the castle...$"
    .string "{UNK_0300AA}A {COLOR}{RED}sanctuary{COLOR}{WHITE}? Hm... The {COLOR}{RED}minister{COLOR}{WHITE}'s fairy\n"
    .string "tales mention a sanctuary, I think...$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}{PLAYER}, look!\n"
    .string "See how that doorway glows?\n"
    .string "Could that be the door that\n"
    .string "leads to the {COLOR}{RED}sanctuary{COLOR}{WHITE}?\n"
    .string "Nobody in the castle seems able\n"
    .string "to see it but you and me...\n"
    .string "Let's go! Quickly!$"
    .string "{UNK_0300A3}The doorway to the {COLOR}{RED}elemental\n"
    .string "sanctuary{COLOR}{WHITE} is in the castle courtyard?\n"
    .string "All we adults see is just another\n"
    .string "ordinary wall... Incredible!\n"
    .string "Please, just gather the remaining two\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{GREEN}elements{COLOR}{WHITE} and repair the {COLOR}{GREEN}sacred sword{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "I'm counting on you, {PLAYER}.\n"
    .string "Never forget that.$"
    .string "{UNK_0300A9}Oh, ho! The doorway was indeed in the\n"
    .string "garden? My grandmother was right!\n"
    .string "Well, my family has always been known\n"
    .string "for its honesty above all else.\n"
    .string "But I still can't understand...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Why is it that children can see the\n"
    .string "Picori and the doorway, but I cannot?$"
    .string "{UNK_041007}{COLOR}{RED}Vaati{COLOR}{WHITE}! What are you doing there?$"
    .byte 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0x1c, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x1d, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x2b, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0xf8, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x0d, 0x02, 0x00, 0x00, 0x0e, 0x02, 0x00, 0x00, 0x0f, 0x02, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00
    .string "Wh-wh-what?!?$"
    .string "{UNK_03020E}{COLOR}{YELLOW}...   ...   \n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "O young one...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Child who seeks to aid\n"
    .string "the princess of Hyrule...\n"
    .string "My name is Gustaf...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "I was king of Hyrule, countless\n"
