    .string "Stand before me...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Only then will the path open\n"
    .string "to you.$"
    .string "Hmph! Was that...just a dream?\n"
    .string "He said he was a king of Hyrule.\n"
    .string "Wait! Look at your {COLOR}{GREEN}map{COLOR}{WHITE}, {PLAYER}.\n"
    .string "There's some kind of mark on it.\n"
    .string "Hm. I guess that means it wasn't\n"
