    .string "with the power of the elements{COLOR}{WHITE}...\n"
    .string "Yes, there seems to be a pedestal for\n"
    .string "your sword right in the middle there.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Whoa! You just {COLOR}{YELLOW}split in two{COLOR}{WHITE}! So this\n"
    .string "is the {COLOR}{YELLOW}power of the White Sword{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "I guess you can double yourself like\n"
    .string "that anytime you see those panels...$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}Hmmmm...\n"
    .string "This inscription... It says...\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{YELLOW}Focus power in your blade and\n"
    .string "stand on the glowing tile...$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Hey, where are you going, {PLAYER}?!\n"
    .string "We must go through the door we opened!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Hey, {PLAYER}, you've gone too far!\n"
    .string "Just step on those glowing panels!$"
