, 0x0f, 0x00, 0x00, 0x3e, 0x0f, 0x00, 0x00, 0x3f, 0x0f, 0x00, 0x00, 0x40, 0x0f, 0x00, 0x00, 0x41, 0x0f, 0x00, 0x00, 0x42, 0x0f, 0x00, 0x00, 0x43, 0x0f, 0x00, 0x00, 0x44, 0x0f, 0x00, 0x00, 0xce, 0x0f, 0x00, 0x00, 0x2c, 0x10, 0x00, 0x00, 0x24, 0x12, 0x00, 0x00, 0x70, 0x12, 0x00, 0x00, 0xa1, 0x12, 0x00, 0x00, 0xe6, 0x13, 0x00, 0x00, 0x30, 0x15, 0x00, 0x00, 0xbd, 0x15, 0x00, 0x00, 0xd7, 0x15, 0x00, 0x00, 0x41, 0x16, 0x00, 0x00, 0x51, 0x16, 0x00, 0x00, 0xb2, 0x16, 0x00, 0x00, 0xcc, 0x16, 0x00, 0x00, 0xcd, 0x16, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00
    .string "{UNK_03008E}Hmmm... How interesting... Look at the\n"
    .string "images on the stained glass...\n"
    .string "I bet those pictures show us where\n"
    .string "the {COLOR}{GREEN}light force{COLOR}{WHITE} is hidden...$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E8}{UNK_04100E}Ah ha ha haaaa...\n"
    .string "Ezlo, you really are too kind.\n"
    .string "First, you give me my {COLOR}{GREEN}magic cap{COLOR}{WHITE},\n"
    .string "and then you guide me here!\n"
    .string "You've been far too generous, but\n"
    .string "now, I no longer have any use for you.$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E8}{UNK_04100E}He ha ha ha ha... At last, I finally\n"
    .string "know the location of the {COLOR}{GREEN}light force{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}{PLAYER}! Wake up! Can't you\n"
    .string "wake up, {PLAYER}!?$"
    .string "{UNK_03008E}{COLOR}{RED}Vaati {COLOR}{WHITE}disguised himself as the king\n"
    .string "to search for the {COLOR}{GREEN}light force{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "When he learned of this place, he\n"
    .string "waited for us to reforge the blade.\n"
    .string "If that stained glass is accurate,\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{YELLOW}Princess Zelda holds the light force{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "Vaati will do whatever it takes to\n"
    .string "steal that power from her!\n"
    .string "If he succeeds, we may never be able\n"
    .string "to return the princess to normal!\n"
    .string "We've wasted too much time, {PLAYER}!\n"
    .string "We must stop Vaati!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E8}Ha ha ha!\n"
    .string "You ARE persistent, aren't you?$"
    .string "Heh heh heh heh heh heh...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "So, you've come to stop my little\n"
    .string "ceremony. Well, you're too late.\n"
    .string "A mere {COLOR}{YELLOW}three more chimes of the bell{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "will bring the ceremony to its end!\n"
    .string "And with the third toll of the bell,\n"
    .string "I will become like a {COLOR}{RED}god{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "And your precious {COLOR}{RED}Princess Zelda{COLOR}{WHITE} will\n"
    .string "be nothing more than cold, dead stone.$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}There's no time! Quickly, {PLAYER},\n"
    .string "to the roof!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Did you hear that, {PLAYER}?\n"
    .string "Hurry! There are {COLOR}{YELLOW}only two chimes left{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}Another bell has tolled...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{YELLOW}Just one more chime{COLOR}{WHITE}, and all our\n"
    .string "work will have been for naught!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}{PLAYER}! No, it can't be! The bell has\n"
    .string "rung for a third time!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E8}Hmph! Just a few more moments, and the\n"
    .string "ceremony would have been complete.\n"
    .string "You really are obsessed with stopping\n"
    .string "me, aren't you? Ah, very well.\n"
    .string "I have not yet drained all of the {COLOR}{GREEN}light\n"
    .string "force{COLOR}{WHITE} housed in Princess Zelda.\n"
    .string "But what I have should suffice...\n"
    .string "I shall be transformed! Unstoppable!\n"
    .string "But let me first attend to the pesky\n"
    .string "worms who would trifle with me...$"
    .string "Hmph!$"
    .string "{UNK_041000}{UNK_0301E9}I will have no more of you interfering\n"
    .string "with my plans!\n"
    .string "Let me show you true power!!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_04100E}{UNK_03009B}Well, you seem to have some fight in\n"
    .string "you. I commend your bravery.\n"
    .string "But you will not survive...THIS!!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_04100E}{UNK_03009B}Grrrrr.....\n"
    .string "I am filled with a power that you cannot\n"
    .string "begin to understand! Do you think that\n"
    .string "puny sword will save you from ME?!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}You did it! Impressive! Now, quickly!\n"
    .string "We must break the curse on {COLOR}{RED}Zelda{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "What... What is this madness?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "I have the power of a god!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "I have unstoppable might!!!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "How could I lose to a child?!?$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E3}{PLAYER}, thank you so much for\n"
    .string "saving me.\n"
    .string "When I was turned to stone, I saw\n"
    .string "visions of you, as if in a dream.$"
    .string "{UNK_0301DF}Oh! That {COLOR}{GREEN}shield{COLOR}{WHITE}! I...remember it...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "You still have it? That's so sweet!\n"
    .string "I knew I could count on you.$"
    .string "{UNK_030090}It looks like the curse has been\n"
    .string "broken. I'm glad we made it in time.$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}No! The castle's collapsing!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "It's too dangerous here. Quickly!\n"
    .string "We must escape from the castle!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}Hrmm... The door is blocked! We have no\n"
    .string "choice... Head back to the {COLOR}{RED}sanctuary{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "{UNK_03008D}So, {PLAYER}! Now that you have the\n"
    .string "power of the {COLOR}{GREEN}Four Sword{COLOR}{WHITE}...\n"
    .string "you must return {COLOR}{RED}Princess Zelda {COLOR}{WHITE}to\n"
    .string "normal!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_03009B}{PLAYER}! And you, Ezlo!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "I will not let you escape this place\n"
    .string "alive...\n"
    .string "Witness the power of Vaati's Wrath!\n"
    .string "I have transcended! I am all there is!\n"
    .string "Allow me to give you a taste of pure\n"
    .string "power, of unstoppable might!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E8}Heh heh heh heh...\n"
    .string "You will not escape, boy.\n"
    .string "Now, you will see the true power of\n"
    .string "the {COLOR}{GREEN}light force{COLOR}{WHITE}...\n"
    .string "For I have become Vaati,\n"
    .string "the master of this world!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_041007}Fool! I... But the {COLOR}{GREEN}light force{COLOR}{WHITE}...\n"
    .string "My power... I had such power...$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E3}{PLAYER}, thank goodness you're\n"
    .string "safe...\n"
    .string "You defeated Vaati...\n"
    .string "You were so brave!\n"
    .string "But we've lost so much...\n"
    .string "The castle... All those people...$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E7}What's this?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "The curse... Defeating Vaati seems to\n"
    .string "have broken the curse he cast upon me!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E6}Allow me to introduce myself\n"
    .string "to you, Princess Zelda.\n"
    .string "My name is {COLOR}{RED}Ezlo{COLOR}{WHITE}, master of Minish\n"
    .string "lore and sorcery.\n"
    .string "The mage's cap was my creation.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "But its limitless power has caused\n"
    .string "nothing but trouble for your kind.\n"
    .string "Is there any way you can forgive me?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "I know many have fallen, and much of\n"
    .string "the castle has been destroyed...\n"
    .string "But it is too soon to give\n"
    .string "in to despair.\n"
    .string "The curse on me is broken, and Zelda\n"
    .string "still possesses some of the light force.\n"
    .string "Perhaps, together, we can do\n"
    .string "something to make things right.$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E6}If one with a just heart wears this\n"
    .string "cap, things can be made right again.$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E5}Princess Zelda!\n"
    .string "Let your wishes be made real!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E6}Hmm-hmm!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "The hat is falling apart. It's\n"
    .string "overflowing with the power of life!\n"
    .string "The hat has the power to turn the\n"
    .string "thoughts of its wearer into reality.\n"
    .string "Vaati's heart was filled with evil, and\n"
    .string "that was reflected in what he became.\n"
    .string "But it seems that Zelda's pure heart,\n"
    .string "coupled with the hat's power...\n"
    .string "...has created a miracle!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E6}Hmm... It looks like the time for us\n"
    .string "to part has come.\n"
    .string "The Minish Door opens but once every\n"
    .string "century, and soon, it must close.\n"
    .string "I must leave you both now and return\n"
    .string "to my homeland.\n"
    .string "I know I've caused you much suffering,\n"
    .string "but the evil one's power has withered.\n"
    .string "The power of Princess Zelda herself\n"
    .string "has restored the light to Hyrule.$"
    .string "{UNK_041000}Well, {PLAYER}, my journey with you\n"
    .string "has been exciting, to say the least.\n"
    .string "In fact, I'm...more than just a little\n"
    .string "sad that we must part w"
    .string "ays now.$"
    .string "{UNK_041000}Please, accept this...$"
    .string "Heh... You know, I've never actually\n"
    .string "seen you wearing a cap until now!\tx\n"
    .string "{UNK_0301E6}It suits you, little hero.\n"
    .string "\tx$"
    .string "Take care...\n"
    .string "\tx$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E0}{UNK_04100E}Look! The castle! All the people who\n"
    .string "had been turned to stone!\n"
    .string "They're all back to normal!$"
    .string "Farewell, my friend...\n"
    .string "\tx$"
    .string "$"
