    .string "   {CHOICE_FF}Sure   {CHOICE_1F10}No, thanks$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E5}Hm... I've never seen an outfit like\n"
    .string "that before. Are you a...human?\n"
    .string "Oh, my! It's been quite some time\n"
    .string "since any humans came here.\n"
    .string "My name is {COLOR}{RED}Festari{COLOR}{WHITE}. I watch the abbey,\n"
    .string "as well as the shrine to the north.\n"
    .string "You...seem to be having some trouble\n"
    .string "with our language, don't you?\n"
    .string "You could use a {COLOR}{GREEN}Jabber Nut{COLOR}{WHITE}. It will\n"
    .string "allow you to understand our tongue.\n"
    .string "You should be able to find one in\n"
    .string "the barrel house just south of here.$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E5}You wish to go to the {COLOR}{RED}shrine{COLOR}{WHITE}?\n"
    .string "Very well. This way...$"
    .string "Vile beasts have settled in recently.\n"
    .string "Be careful: it is quite dangerous.$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E5}You retrieved the {COLOR}{GREEN}Earth Element {COLOR}{WHITE}from\n"
    .string "that fiend-infested shrine?\n"
    .string "Incredible!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Humans are amazing creatures.\n"
    .string "The elder is sure to be amazed, too.$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E5}So you're on a quest to restore the\n"
    .string "sacred blade so you can save the\n"
    .string "princess? Yeah, I'm sure you'll\n"
    .string "manage...$"
    .string "{UNK_0301E5}So you've eaten the {COLOR}{GREEN}Jabber Nut{COLOR}{WHITE},\n"
    .string "and now you can understand us?\n"
    .string "...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{UNK_071F1C}$"
    .string "Sorry, but I know little about {COLOR}{GREEN}swords{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "I'm sure the {COLOR}{RED}elder{COLOR}{WHITE} can help you.$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "Oh, {PLAYER}.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "This must be the {COLOR}{GREEN}Jabber Nut {COLOR}{WHITE}Festari\n"
    .string "told you about.\n"
    .string "Well, you'd better eat it if you plan\n"
    .string "on making any progress at all.$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_030203}Pico riki poko ti po!$"
    .string "{UNK_030203}So you've eaten the {COLOR}{GREEN}Jabber Nut{COLOR}{WHITE} and\n"
    .string "now you can understand us...\n"
    .string "The {COLOR}{RED}elder {COLOR}{WHITE}said that humans can no\n"
    .string "longer see us as they once could.\n"
    .string "It's amazing that you can see us.$"
    .string "{UNK_030203}This is where we cultivate {COLOR}{YELLOW}Pico Blooms{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "The {COLOR}{GREEN}Picolyte {COLOR}{WHITE}sold in the human town is\n"
    .string "made from the {COLOR}{YELLOW}nectar of our plants{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "We sneak into town at night and leave\n"
    .string "it there for the humans to find.$"
    .string "South of here, there's a house\n"
    .string "shaped like a barrel.\n"
    .string "Inside, you will find a {COLOR}{GREEN}Jabber Nut{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "If you eat this {COLOR}{GREEN}Jabber Nut{COLOR}{WHITE}, you will be\n"
    .string "able to understand the Minish tongue.$"
