    .string "Ruff! Ruff!$"
    .string "{UNK_03021A}Honestly! Where did Dad go this time?!?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "I leave for just a few minutes, and he\n"
    .string "locks up the ranch and takes off!$"
    .string "I lost my key, and I can't get inside.\n"
    .string "And the {COLOR}{GREEN}spare key{COLOR}{WHITE}'s inside the house!$"
    .string "{UNK_03021A}What a pain. And I was thinking of\n"
    .string "going into town to sell {COLOR}{GREEN}Lon Lon Milk{COLOR}{WHITE}.$"
    .string "Oh! Our one and only spare key!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "I don't know how you got this, but\n"
    .string "I can't thank you enough!\n"
    .string "Tell me your name, sonny.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{UNK_041206}$"
    .string "? That's a great name.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "If you ever need to go to {COLOR}{RED}Lake Hylia{COLOR}{WHITE},\n"
    .string "feel free to cut through our house.$"
    .string "You really helped me out, sonny.\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "If you ever want to go to {COLOR}{RED}Lake Hylia{COLOR}{WHITE},\n"
    .string "use the shortcut out behind our ranch.$"
    .string "{UNK_03021A}Thank you, {PLAYER}. Now, I can\n"
    .string "finally get back into my house.\n"
    .string "Well, I'd better be going. I have a\n"
    .string "lot to do before I can leave town.$"
    .string "Nayhayhayyyy...$"
    .string "$"
    .string "Well! If it isn't {PLAYER}! I just\n"
    .string "finished milking our pride and joy.\n"
    .string "I'll tell you what, {PLAYER}... Because\n"
    .string "you did us such a big favor...\n"
    .string "I'll sell you some milk at our special,\n"
    .string "friends-only price.\n"
    .string "If you ever need a {COLOR}{YELLOW}quick burst of\n"
    .string "strength{COLOR}{WHITE}, just drink it up!\n"
    .string "And if you run out, just bring\n"
    .string "your empty bottle back for a refill!\n"
    .string "Buy some {COLOR}{GREEN}Lon Lon Milk {COLOR}{WHITE}for 30 Rupees?\n"
    .string "   {CHOICE_FF}Sure   {CHOICE_2014}No, thanks$"
    .string "Here you go! Have some freshly\n"
    .string "squeezed {COLOR}{GREEN}Lon Lon Milk{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "Here you go! Have some...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Whoops!! You don't have an {COLOR}{GREEN}empty\n"
    .string "bottle{COLOR}{WHITE}! Too bad...$"
    .string "Drop in for a visit the next time\n"
    .string "you're in the neighborhood.$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_03021A}Thank you very much, {PLAYER}.\n"
    .string "Come visit us again!$"
    .string "Bray-hey-hey-hey-hey...$"
    .string "Moooo!$"
