    .string "{UNK_030204}We forest {COLOR}{RED}Minish{COLOR}{GREEN} {COLOR}{WHITE}are good at\n"
    .string "growing plants and making tools.\n"
    .string "The {COLOR}{GREEN}Minish Berries{COLOR}{WHITE} we grow here often\n"
    .string "contain items that please the humans.$"
    .string "{UNK_0301F9}There's a weird guy outside the village\n"
    .string "who {COLOR}{YELLOW}invents all kinds of tools{COLOR}{WHITE}"
    .string ".\n"
    .string "He came to the village a while ago. We\n"
    .string "thought maybe he was back for good.\n"
    .string "But all he said was {COLOR}{YELLOW}{QT}Got any {COLOR}{GREEN}milk{COLOR}{YELLOW}?{QT}{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "Maybe he was thirsty or something.$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FE}There's a weird guy outside the village\n"
    .string "who {COLOR}{YELLOW}invents all kinds of tools{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "He came to the village a while ago. We\n"
    .string "thought maybe he was back for good.\n"
    .string "But all he said was {COLOR}{YELLOW}{QT}Got any {COLOR}{GREEN}blue\n"
    .string "potions{COLOR}{YELLOW}?{QT} {COLOR}{WHITE}Maybe he caught a cold...$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_0301F7}Sometimes it's a flower seed, and\n"
    .string "sometimes it's a stone.\n"
    .string "We hide our lucky items in all sorts of\n"
    .string "unexpected places.\n"
    .string "But the real trick is making it tough\n"
    .string "for humans to notice!$"
    .string "{UNK_030203}Sometimes it's a flower seed, and\n"
    .string "sometimes it's a stone.\n"
    .string "We hide our lucky items in all sorts of\n"
    .string "unexpected places.\n"
    .string "But the real trick is making it tough\n"
    .string "for humans to notice!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FD}I've been getting better at disguising\n"
    .string "things so that humans won't notice 'em!\n"
    .string "I love my job!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_030205}Wow! Good job finding this place! There\n"
    .string "aren't many people who visit me here.$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FE}Hehhe! Great! Let's fuse now!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FF}Hehe! That's why I can't get enough\n"
    .string "of Kinstone fusion!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FD}Awww... Really?$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_0301F8}You've heard of travelers who find a\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{GREEN}Kinstone {COLOR}{WHITE}and get really lucky?\n"
    .string "Well, that's all thanks to items made\n"
    .string "by us {COLOR}{RED}Minish{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "You see, we thrive on making humans\n"
    .string "happy. It gives us energy.\n"
    .string "But we only do it in secret!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301F8}You've heard of travelers who pick up a\n"
    .string "stone and find something under it?\n"
    .string "Well, those items were actually left\n"
    .string "there by us {COLOR}{RED}Minish{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "You see, we thrive on making humans\n"
    .string "happy. It gives us energy.\n"
    .string "But we only do it in secret!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301F8}You've heard of travelers who pick up a\n"
    .string "stone and find something under it?\n"
    .string "Well, those items were actually left\n"
    .string "there by us {COLOR}{RED}Minish{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "We live for making humans happy, but\n"
    .string "we only do it in secret!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FB}Our ancestors, the ancient {COLOR}{RED}Minish{COLOR}{WHITE},\n"
    .string "used the portal between our worlds.\n"
    .string "It brought them into the human world,\n"
    .string "and they settled in this forest.$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FB}Our ancestors, the ancient {COLOR}{RED}Minish{COLOR}{WHITE},\n"
    .string "used the portal between our worlds.\n"
    .string "It brought them here, into the human\n"
    .string "world, and they settled in this forest.\n"
    .string "The {COLOR}{RED}elder {COLOR}{WHITE}says our cultures have\n"
    .string "changed much since those old days.$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_030203}If you want to reforge that sword, you\n"
    .string "will need the help of an expert smith!\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}Master Melari{COLOR}{WHITE} and his seven\n"
    .string "apprentices can help you.\n"
    .string "They live in the mountains, where they\n"
    .string "can find all the ore they need.\n"
    .string "I'm sure the {COLOR}{RED}elder {COLOR}{WHITE}would tell you about\n"
    .string "him if you asked.$"
    .string "{UNK_030203}If you want that sword reforged, you\n"
    .string "should see {COLOR}{RED}Melari{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "He and his apprentices are skilled in\n"
    .string "the arts of metalworking.\n"
    .string "That's why they live in the mountain:\n"
    .string "so they can be close to the ore!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FA}So how was old {COLOR}{RED}Melari{COLOR}{WHITE}?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "And were his apprentices singing their\n"
    .string "usual work song?$"
    .string "Pico ricopi picoco copi!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_0301F9}There are so many monsters around\n"
    .string "these woods lately!\n"
    .string "The elder said that even the {COLOR}{RED}shrine {COLOR}{WHITE}to\n"
    .string "the north is filled with monsters now!$"
    .string "{UNK_030200}You fought all the monsters and took\n"
    .string "the {COLOR}{GREEN}Earth Element{COLOR}{WHITE} from the altar?\n"
    .string "You humans are amazing.$"
    .string "{UNK_030200}You fought the monsters all the way to\n"
    .string "the altar to get the {COLOR}{GREEN}Earth Element{COLOR}{WHITE}?\n"
    .string "Wow, humans are amazing!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_030202}Do you know about {COLOR}{GREEN}Kinstone pieces{COLOR}{WHITE}?\n"
    .string "They're all the rage among humans now.$"
    .string "{UNK_030202}Do you know about {COLOR}{GREEN}Kinstone pieces{COLOR}{WHITE}?\n"
    .string "They're all the rage among humans now.$"
    .string "{UNK_030202}Do you know about {COLOR}{GREEN}Kinstone pieces{COLOR}{WHITE}?\n"
    .string "They're all the rage among humans now.$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_0301F8}Hey, nice clothes...\n"
    .string "I want to wear human clothes, too!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301F9}I was born and raised here, so I don't\n"
    .string "know much about the outside world.\n"
    .string "I hear there are HUGE green monsters\n"
    .string "out there in the woods.\n"
    .string "I can't believe you made it through\n"
    .string "there alive! You must be really brave!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301F9}That's it! I've decided!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "When I grow up, I'm going to be human!\n"
    .string "...I wonder how I'll do that...$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FA}I'm getting set to leave for town and\n"
    .string "visit some of my Minish friends there.$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FB}We {COLOR}{RED}Minish {COLOR}{WHITE}live in Hyrule Town and other\n"
    .string "places, too--not just in these woods.$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FC}Had you never seen any {COLOR}{RED}Minish {COLOR}{WHITE}before\n"
    .string "you came here?\n"
    .string "Really? That's so strange.\n"
    .string "We Minish live all over the place!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FE}We {COLOR}{RED}Minish {COLOR}{WHITE}live in Hyrule Town and other\n"
    .string "places, too--not just in these woods.$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_030203}You probably haven't noticed, but lots\n"
    .string "of {COLOR}{RED}Minish {COLOR}{WHITE}live right in {COLOR}{RED}Hyrule Town{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "{UNK_030202}Maybe I should just get out of this\n"
    .string "sleepy little town and move to the city.\n"
    .string "Or maybe I should go to the mountains.\n"
    .string "The folks out there seem to have fun!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FB}I received a letter from my friend who\n"
    .string "lives in the town library!\n"
    .string "I wish I could live in town, too...$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_030205}Hello!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "We're doing cutting-edge research on\n"
    .string "Pico Blooms here.\n"
    .string "You see that plant with the little bud?\n"
    .string "We're working on ways to improve it!$"
    .string "{UNK_030202}I need {COLOR}{GREEN}milk {COLOR}{WHITE}to continue my improvements\n"
    .string "on this Pico Bloom.\n"
    .string "I wish someone would bring me some.$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FD}Wow, thanks!\n"
    .string "Now I can continue my research!\n"
    .string "Come on back when this\n"
    .string "flower blossoms!$"
    .string "{UNK_030202}My new Pico Bloom hasn't blossomed yet.\n"
    .string "Come back soon, though.$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FF}Look! I succeeded in growing a {COLOR}{YELLOW}Yellow\n"
    .string "Pico Bloom{COLOR}{WHITE}! It's all thanks to you!\n"
    .string "I'm so grateful for all your help!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FC}I am working on my next Pico Bloom\n"
    .string "enhancement...\n"
    .string "All I need is some {COLOR}{GREEN}Mt. Crenel Mineral\n"
    .string "Water{COLOR}{WHITE} to complete it.\n"
    .string "But the mountain is so far away, and I\n"
    .string "don't know how to get any.\n"
    .string "I wish someone would bring me some.$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FD}Wow, thanks! This is just what I\n"
    .string "needed to complete my research!\n"
    .string "Come back when the bud blossoms!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FF}Look! I succeeded in growing a {COLOR}{YELLOW}Blue\n"
    .string "Pico Bloom{COLOR}{WHITE}! It's all thanks to you!\n"
    .string "I'm so grateful for all your help!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FC}I am working on my next Pico Bloom\n"
    .string "enhancement...\n"
    .string "But I need a {COLOR}{GREEN}red potion{COLOR}{WHITE} to finish. If\n"
    .string "only I knew where some could be found.\n"
    .string "I wish someone would bring me some.$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FD}Wow, thanks! This is just what I needed\n"
    .string "to make that bud blossom!\n"
    .string "Come back and see how it turns out!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FF}Look! I succeeded in growing an\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{YELLOW}Orange Pico Bloom{COLOR}{WHITE}, thanks to your help!\n"
    .string "I'm so grateful to you!$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FA}I'm taking a break from my research,\n"
    .string "but I have lots of good ideas.\n"
    .string "Super Pico Bloom...\n"
    .string "Hyper Pico Bloom...\n"
    .string "Cyber Pico Bloom...\n"
    .string "Which one should I work on first?$"
    .string "{UNK_0301FB}Hey! What've you got there?\n"
    .string "Is that {COLOR}{GREEN}Lon Lon Milk{COLOR}{WHITE}?\n"
    .string "Did you bring it for me?\n"
    .string "{CHOICE_FF}Yes   {CHOICE_214E}No$"
