    .string "There should be some {COLOR}{RED}Minish{COLOR}{WHITE} living here\n"
    .string "in this forest.\n"
    .string "Eh? Who are the {COLOR}{RED}Minish{COLOR}{WHITE}? Ah, yes,\n"
    .string "how silly of me!\n"
    .string "You humans call them {QT}{COLOR}{RED}Picori{COLOR}{WHITE},{QT} but they\n"
    .string "refer to themselves as the {COLOR}{RED}Minish{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "Strange how, in the world of humans,\n"
    .string "only this forest has kept the name...\n"
    .string "Anyhow, deep in the forest they built a\n"
    .string "tiny village, where many now live.\n"
    .string "But if we're to enter the village, we'll\n"
    .string "have to make you a touch smaller first.\n"
    .string "Look for a tree stump. Then, I can\n"
    .string "shrink you to the size of the {QT}{COLOR}{RED}Picori{COLOR}{WHITE}.{QT}$"
    .string "{UNK_030092}{UNK_041000}Hold on for a moment, my boy! We've\n"
    .string "stumbled across something important!\n"
    .string "The world of the {COLOR}{RED}Minish{COLOR}{WHITE} is very small.\n"
    .string "You're far too big to meet them now.\n"
    .string "Eh? Who are the {COLOR}{RED}Minish{COLOR}{WHITE}? Ah, yes! Silly\n"
    .string "me! Allow me to explain...\n"
    .string "You humans call them {QT}{COLOR}{RED}Picori{COLOR}{WHITE},{QT} but they\n"
    .string "refer to themselves as the {COLOR}{RED}Minish{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "Strange how, in the world of humans,\n"
    .string "only this forest has kept that name...\n"
    .string "Anyhow, deep in the forest they built a\n"
    .string "tiny village, where many now live.\n"
    .string "But if we're to enter the village, we'll\n"
    .string "have to make you a touch smaller first.\n"
    .string "Look at that. At first glance, it\n"
    .string "appears to be a mere stump, yes?\n"
    .string "No! That stump is a {COLOR}{YELLOW}portal{COLOR}{WHITE} used by\n"
    .string "people long ago to adjust their size!\n"
    .string "With my help, you can use it to {COLOR}{YELLOW}shrink\n"
    .string "down to Minish size{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "Just stand on the stump and press {RIGHT}\n"
    .string "to shrink.\n"
    .string "To return to normal, stand next to the\n"
    .string "stump and press {RIGHT}.\n"
    .string "Get me up there, and we'll give\n"
    .string "it a try.$"
    .string "Welcome to the world through the\n"
    .string "eyes of the Minish!\n"
    .string "Now, aren't you glad you saved me?\n"
    .string "No need to thank me, though!\n"
    .string "Portals that reduce your size are {COLOR}{YELLOW}all\n"
    .string "around, in different shapes and sizes{COLOR}{WHITE}.{COLOR}{YELLOW}\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{WHITE}If you want to return to normal, stand\n"
    .string "next to a portal and press {RIGHT}.\n"
    .string "But there is one thing you must know:\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{YELLOW}being Minish-sized is full of dangers{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "Mere puddles at your normal size\n"
    .string "are bottomless swamps to the Minish.\n"
    .string "And as your companion, if anything bad\n"
    .string "happens to you, it happens to me, too!\n"
    .string "So proceed with caution, my lad! If not\n"
    .string "for your sake, then for my own!$"
    .byte 0xff, 0xff, 0x58, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x59, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x5a, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0xe0, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x28, 0x01, 0x00, 0x00, 0x57, 0x01, 0x00, 0x00, 0x58, 0x01, 0x00, 0x00, 0x59, 0x01, 0x00, 0x00, 0x5a, 0x01, 0x00, 0x00, 0x5b, 0x01, 0x00, 0x00, 0x5c, 0x01, 0x00, 0x00, 0x5d, 0x01, 0x00, 0x00, 0x5e, 0x01, 0x00, 0x00, 0xdc, 0x03, 0x00, 0x00, 0x93, 0x05, 0x00, 0x00, 0xcb, 0x05, 0x00, 0x00, 0x19, 0x06, 0x00, 0x00, 0xc1, 0x06, 0x00, 0x00, 0x2b, 0x08, 0x00, 0x00, 0x68, 0x09, 0x00, 0x00, 0x96, 0x09, 0x00, 0x00, 0xe1, 0x09, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00
    .string "The swamp in {COLOR}{RED}Castor Wilds{COLOR}{WHITE} is\n"
    .string "bottomless...I say.\n"
    .string "To get across that swamp, you'll need\n"
    .string "to {COLOR}{YELLOW}run as swiftly as the wind blows{COLOR}{WHITE}...$"
    .string "A dark room settles my soul...I say.\n"
    .string "Do not turn on the lights...I say.$"
    .string "Oh, dear. You found me out!\n"
    .string "Don't tell anyone!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "Hello. I am Percy, poet laureate\n"
    .string "of Hyrule.\n"
    .string "And you are {PLAYER}? Oh, no,\n"
    .string "no! The pleasure is mine!\n"
    .string "I travel all over the realm, writing\n"
    .string "verse wherever I go.\n"
    .string "But here I am, returning after a long\n"
    .string "absence only to find the road blocked.\n"
    .string "It wouldn't feel like such a waste if\n"
    .string "I hadn't lost half of my {COLOR}{GREEN}Kinstone{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "When misfortune rains down upon\n"
    .string "my head, it pours in torrents!\n"
    .string "I think {COLOR}{YELLOW}I may have dropped it in the\n"
    .string "inn{COLOR}{WHITE} I stayed at last night...\n"
    .string "I see no other course than to put\n"
    .string "these tragic events to verse.\n"
    .string "  {COLOR}{YELLOW}I see stars beyond the rainbow,\n"
    .string "  But I cannot reach them.\n"
    .string "  Though the stone I lost is small,\n"
    .string "  Large was its place in my heart.$"
    .string "My way home is blocked. Alas!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "And making matters worse, I lost one of\n"
    .string "my {COLOR}{GREEN}stone fragments{COLOR}{WHITE} in my travels.\n"
    .string "When misfortune rains down upon\n"
    .string "my head, it pours in torrents!\n"
    .string "I wonder if I dropped that stone\n"
    .string "fragment {COLOR}{YELLOW}in the inn{COLOR}{WHITE} last night.\n"
    .string "I see no other course than to put\n"
    .string "these tragic events to verse.\n"
    .string "  {COLOR}{YELLOW}I see stars beyond the rainbow,\n"
    .string "  But I cannot reach them.\n"
    .string "  Though the stone I lost is small,\n"
    .string "  Large was its place in my heart.$"
    .string "Unfortunately, I only have one\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{GREEN}fragment{COLOR}{WHITE}. I'm sorry.$"
    .string "Oh, my! That {COLOR}{GREEN}fragment{COLOR}{WHITE} looks just like\n"
    .string "mine! They might even fit together!$"
    .string "Oh, perfect! They fit!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "That's it! I've got it now!\n"
    .string "The perfect verse!\n"
    .string "  {COLOR}{YELLOW}Apart or whole,\n"
    .string "  These two are one.\n"
    .string "  Two lost and broken halves,\n"
    .string "  Like me and my beloved.$"
    .string "Oh, dear! {PLAYER}!\n"
    .string "Won't you listen to my verse?\n"
    .string "When I finally returned to my home,\n"
    .string "sweet home, a stranger was there!\n"
    .string "I'm an extremely shy person, and I just\n"
    .string "can't talk to someone I don't know!\n"
    .string "So...I had to put my feelings to verse!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "  {COLOR}{YELLOW}While I was gone, did you break in\n"
    .string "  To practice your thieving art?\n"
    .string "  Even if you rob my home,\n"
    .string "  You can never steal my heart.$"
    .string "Oh, my! {PLAYER}! Thanks to you, I can\n"
    .string "finally go back in my house.\n"
    .string "It's been totally rearranged, but I\n"
    .string "think it's a good look!\n"
    .string "I've put my feelings of gratitude\n"
    .string "to verse...\n"
    .string "  {COLOR}{YELLOW}The way made safe, I came back home\n"
    .string "  To find me inside, all alone.\n"
    .string "  In my chest, my poor heart aches,\n"
    .string "  But for you I feel the deepest thanks!$"
    .string "What? You're going to quit?\n"
    .string "Well, come again.$"
    .string "Oh, {PLAYER}!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Did you come all the way here just to\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{YELLOW}fuse Kinstones{COLOR}{WHITE} with me?$"
    .string "Oh, just a moment...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "My dresser is entirely stuffed full\n"
    .string "of these icky blue seashells.\n"
    .string "Would you clean them out for me?\n"
    .string "They're so...smelly. Please?$"
    .byte 0xff, 0x44, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x45, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x1d, 0x02, 0x00, 0x00, 0xb3, 0x02, 0x00, 0x00, 0x43, 0x03, 0x00, 0x00, 0xbb, 0x03, 0x00, 0x00, 0xed, 0x03, 0x00, 0x00, 0x3a, 0x04, 0x00, 0x00, 0x7d, 0x04, 0x00, 0x00, 0x7e, 0x04, 0x00, 0x00, 0x7f, 0x04, 0x00, 0x00, 0x80, 0x04, 0x00, 0x00, 0x81, 0x04, 0x00, 0x00, 0xa2, 0x06, 0x00, 0x00, 0x12, 0x07, 0x00, 0x00, 0x13, 0x07, 0x00, 0x00, 0x14, 0x07, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00
    .string "Oh! Oh, thank you! You're the one who\n"
    .string "returned me to normal, aren't you?\n"
    .string "I don't know how you did it, but\n"
    .string "I can't thank you enough...\n"
    .string "Listen... Have you seen how strange\n"
    .string "the {COLOR}{RED}king {COLOR}{WHITE}has been lately?\n"
    .string "That's because it's not the king at all!\n"
    .string "It's {COLOR}{RED}Vaati{COLOR}{WHITE}! He's taken over the castle!\n"
    .string "One by one, he turned us all to stone.\n"
    .string "Everyone, cursed by his evil magic...\n"
    .string "Then, the monsters arrived. Even\n"
    .string "paralyzed, I saw it all...\n"
    .string "I only pray it's not too late to undo\n"
    .string "his evil...$"
    .string "{PLAYER}! We need your help!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{RED}Vaati {COLOR}{WHITE}took our petrified princess to\n"
    .string "the roof of the castle...\n"
    .string "He must be planning something fiendish.\n"
    .string "You must stop him!$"
    .string "The real {COLOR}{RED}king of Hyrule {COLOR}{WHITE}must be locked\n"
    .string "up somewhere in the castle...\n"
    .string "Please find him. As soon as we've\n"
    .string "recovered, we'll start looking, too.$"
    .string "Oh! Thank you for restoring me.\n"
    .string "I feel so much better now!\n"
    .string "Don't worry about me. I'll be fine.\n"
    .string "Now, go help the others!$"
    .string "Leave this to us!\n"
    .string "You go save {COLOR}{RED}Princess Zelda{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "Don't worry--we'll protect the king.\n"
    .string "You have to go save {COLOR}{RED}Princess Zelda{COLOR}{WHITE}!$"
    .string "Gah! I hate to admit it, but we're\n"
    .string "just no match for those beasts!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "Oh! {PLAYER}!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Are you the one who broke the\n"
    .string "curse and returned me to normal?\n"
    .string "You've grown quite brave since\n"
    .string "I last saw you, I must say.\n"
    .string "But, oh, how this castle has suffered\n"
    .string "while I was under {COLOR}{RED}Vaati{COLOR}{WHITE}'s curse...\n"
    .string "Is this all the work of one man?\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "As {COLOR}{RED}king of Hyrule{COLOR}{WHITE}, I must do\n"
    .string "something about this villain...\n"
    .string "But... Ah, I'm old, and I would only\n"
    .string "hold you back.\n"
    .string "{PLAYER}, you have the {COLOR}{GREEN}sacred blade{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "now. We must rely on you.\n"
    .string "Please! You must find a way to rescue\n"
    .string "my {COLOR}{RED}Zelda{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "Take this key. You can use it to get\n"
    .string "out of the castle from the basement.$"
    .string "If I were to join you, I fear I would\n"
    .string "only be a hindrance.\n"
    .string "Please, {PLAYER}, you must find a way\n"
    .string "to save my daughter.$"
    .string "$"
