    .byte 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0xff, 0xa0, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0xa1, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0xcb, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0xe7, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x48, 0x01, 0x00, 0x00, 0x9a, 0x01, 0x00, 0x00, 0x1b, 0x02, 0x00, 0x00, 0x49, 0x02, 0x00, 0x00, 0x4a, 0x02, 0x00, 0x00, 0x4b, 0x02, 0x00, 0x00, 0x4c, 0x02, 0x00, 0x00, 0x4d, 0x02, 0x00, 0x00, 0x4e, 0x02, 0x00, 0x00, 0x06, 0x03, 0x00, 0x00, 0x67, 0x05, 0x00, 0x00, 0xd4, 0x05, 0x00, 0x00, 0x25, 0x06, 0x00, 0x00, 0xb1, 0x06, 0x00, 0x00, 0x35, 0x07, 0x00, 0x00, 0x73, 0x07, 0x00, 0x00, 0x38, 0x08, 0x00, 0x00, 0x03, 0x09, 0x00, 0x00, 0x54, 0x0a, 0x00, 0x00, 0x33, 0x0b, 0x00, 0x00, 0xa7, 0x0b, 0x00, 0x00, 0x31, 0x0c, 0x00, 0x00, 0xe9, 0x0c, 0x00, 0x00, 0x7c, 0x0d, 0x00, 0x00, 0xcc, 0x0d, 0x00, 0x00, 0x70, 0x0f, 0x00, 0x00, 0xc4, 0x0f, 0x00, 0x00, 0xed, 0x0f, 0x00, 0x00, 0x0c, 0x10, 0x00, 0x00, 0x5e, 0x10, 0x00, 0x00, 0xa3, 0x10, 0x00, 0x00, 0xf9, 0x10, 0x00, 0x00, 0x8c, 0x11, 0x00, 0x00, 0x16, 0x12, 0x00, 0x00, 0x8c, 0x12, 0x00, 0x00, 0xbc, 0x12, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00
    .string "Here we are, {PLAYER}!\n"
    .string "Doesn't it look fun?\n"
    .string "{UNK_072502}$"
    .string "Come on! Let's look around!$"
    .string "{PLAYER}, there's a storyteller here!\n"
    .string "We should stop and listen to--\n"
    .string "Oh! I wonder what's over there...$"
    .string "So the {COLOR}{RED}Picori {COLOR}{WHITE}ARE real! My father\n"
    .string "always told me they were.\n"
    .string "Oh! Look at that!$"
    .string "Say, wasn't there going to be a {COLOR}{YELLOW}sword-\n"
    .string "fighting tournament{COLOR}{WHITE} at the castle?\n"
    .string "I wonder who won this year...\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "Oh, wow! Over here!$"
    .string "{PLAYER}! Where are you going?\n"
    .string "Over here! This way!$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "$"
    .string "Welcome to the {COLOR}{YELLOW}Picori Festival{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "They say that, every hundred years,\n"
    .string "the Picori come to Hyrule...\n"
    .string "And this is the 100th year, to the day,\n"
    .string "since the last time the Picori were here!$"
    .string "Long, long ago, and then even longer\n"
    .string "before that...\n"
    .string "Evil creatures appeared in the world\n"
    .string "of humans.\n"
    .string "They were powerful, frightening\n"
    .string "beasts, and they created such trouble!\n"
    .string "But then the {COLOR}{RED}Picori{COLOR}{WHITE} came from the sky,\n"
    .string "bringing humans powerful magic.\n"
    .string "With the magic light force and the\n"
    .string "Picori Blade, the beasts were repelled.\n"
    .string "And the world of humans once more\n"
    .string "knew peace, thanks to the Picori.\n"
    .string "So as not to forget our gratitude, we\n"
    .string "hold this festival each year.\n"
    .string "Now, remember, little ones... The Picori\n"
    .string "only appear before good little children.\n"
    .string "If you only do bad deeds, you will\n"
    .string "never get to see them! So be good!$"
    .string "I don't believe in the Picori!\n"
    .string "\n"
    .string "I'm not a kid anymore! I'm too old to\n"
    .string "believe in any stupid old fairy tales!$"
    .string "Do you think I'll really see the Picori\n"
    .string "if I'm on my best behavior all the time?$"
    .string "Come on up! Come one, come all!\n"
    .string "Gather round and have a look-see!\n"
    .string "I'm having a huge sale on all manner\n"
    .string "of delicious and festive vegetables!$"
    .string "Oh, hi! Are you enjoying the festival?\n"
    .string "It's so much fun!\n"
    .string "I'm so happy to be here! And my fresh\n"
    .string "fruits are just delicious! Buy some!$"
    .string "Come one! Come all! Try your luck,\n"
    .string "and win incredible prizes!$"
    .string "Hey, guy, have you ever seen the\n"
    .string "Picori? I saw one just the other day!\n"
    .string "It wore a red cone-shaped hat, and\n"
    .string "it was really small...\n"
    .string "And it was standing inside my dad's\n"
    .string "shoe! I really saw it! I swear!$"
    .string "So, so, so... I've been good all year?\n"
    .string "Like, all year long?\n"
    .string "And you know how the Picori only\n"
    .string "show themselves if you've been good?\n"
    .string "And so, so, so I'm just waiting for\n"
    .string "the Picori to come and play with me.$"
    .string "Only once every hundred years does\n"
    .string "the mystic doorway open.\n"
    .string "This is the door that links the human\n"
    .string "world to the world of the {COLOR}{RED}Picori{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "When this door opens, the {COLOR}{RED}Picori{COLOR}{WHITE} can\n"
    .string "enter our world. And guess what!\n"
    .string "This marks the hundredth year\n"
    .string "since they last appeared here!\n"
    .string "I'm sure something wonderful is\n"
    .string "going to happen at this festival!$"
    .string "Each year, there is a sword-fighting\n"
    .string "tournament at the {COLOR}{YELLOW}Picori Festival{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "This year's tournament is already over.\n"
    .string "I couldn't believe how fast it went!\n"
    .string "I hear {COLOR}{RED}the victor was a mysterious\n"
    .string "man dressed entirely in black{COLOR}{WHITE}.$"
    .string "They say the Picori bring happiness\n"
    .string "to all the humans they meet...\n"
    .string "I wonder when they will bring\n"
    .string "happiness to me...$"
    .string "Are you enjoying yourself, {PLAYER}?\n"
    .string "This is the biggest festival in {COLOR}{RED}Hyrule{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "If you don't stop to enjoy it,\n"
    .string "you'll miss out on all the fun!$"
    .string "I've been on the road for a while.\n"
    .string "I came back in time for the festival.\n"
    .string "It feels wonderful to be back in Hyrule\n"
    .string "again, in this joyous time!\n"
    .string "I... I must put these feelings\n"
    .string "into verse!$"
    .string "I love festivals. It's like seeing your\n"
    .string "town transform into another world!\n"
    .string "It really gives you a chance to think\n"
    .string "about how well we have it here...$"
    .string "People from all over the place come to\n"
    .string "Hyrule Town for the {COLOR}{YELLOW}Picori Festival{COLOR}{WHITE}.$"
    .string "You're the boy from old Master\n"
    .string "Smith's place, right?\n"
    .string "I'm sure you know this, but he's the\n"
    .string "best swordsmith Hyrule's ever seen!\n"
    .string "Every year, I enter the tournament\n"
    .string "trying to win that sword of his.\n"
    .string "I haven't won yet, and maybe I never\n"
    .string "will, but the tournament was awesome!\n"
    .string "The winner this year was a new face.\n"
    .string "I've been wondering where he's from.\n"
    .string "He used some incredible techniques and\n"
    .string "won the whole tourney in record time!$"
    .string "I've been dispatched from {COLOR}{RED}Hyrule Castle{COLOR}{WHITE}\n"
    .string "up north to watch over the festivities.$"
    .string "I've never seen the {COLOR}{RED}Picori {COLOR}{WHITE}before...$"
    .string "You two must be great friends!$"
    .string "I'm going to look for {COLOR}{RED}Picori{COLOR}{WHITE}! Mom said\n"
    .string "there'd be {COLOR}{RED}Picori {COLOR}{WHITE}at the festival!$"
    .string "I saw it! There was a {COLOR}{RED}Picori {COLOR}{WHITE}here\n"
    .string "just a second ago! No, really!$"
    .string "This is my first ever {COLOR}{YELLOW}Picori Festival{COLOR}{WHITE}!\n"
    .string "So...where are all the {COLOR}{RED}Picori{COLOR}{WHITE}, anyway?$"
    .string "Day and night, he's going on and on\n"
    .string "about Picori this and Picori that!\n"
    .string "Doesn't he know they're nothing but a\n"
    .string "silly fairy tale to make kids behave?$"
    .string "I'm just on my way back from seeing\n"
    .string "the tournament at {COLOR}{RED}Hyrule Castle{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "Let me tell you! Watching all those\n"
    .string "sword fights made me hungry!$"
    .string "Phew... Preparing for the festival left\n"
    .string "me absolutely exhausted...\n"
    .string "Still, I'm just enjoying watching\n"
    .string "people have fun.$"
    .string "Hey, hey! Come on up!\n"
    .string "Take a shot! Win a prize!$"
    .string "My sister and I came a long way to see\n"
    .string "the {COLOR}{YELLOW}Picori Festival{COLOR}{WHITE} this year.\n"
    .string "Is it true the festival's named after\n"
